. Also, junior races and an adaptive race.&nbsp;\u003C/p>"},"description":{"en":"\u003Cp>Winter at Swedetown usually begins in late November or early December and can last all the way through April. For you winter enjoyment, Swedetown offers:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>29km of ski trails\u003C/strong>&nbsp;groomed daily for both skating and classic styles. This includes 4.5km of trails lit daily until 8 p.m.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Two snowshoe trails.\u003C/strong>\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Backcountry skiing\u003C/strong>&nbsp;via an ungroomed 4km Backcountry Loop.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Five snowbike loops\u003C/strong>&nbsp;totaling almost 15km.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>A sledding hill&nbsp;\u003C/strong>&ndash; fun for all ages.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>A chalet\u003C/strong> with bathrooms, a changing room, lounge, and concessions\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>"},"region":"Michigan","country":"USA","groups":[{"groupId":"NordicTrails","groupName":"Nordic Trails","groupBounds":[[-88.5212724714388,47.2320506720058],[-88.4606979292655,47.25044931272848]]},{"groupId":"FatbikeTrails","groupOrder":1,"groupName":"Fatbike Trails","groupBounds":[[-88.49447453168558,47.236610672004566],[-88.46406524382476,47.24558931272977]]},{"groupId":"Multi-useTrails","groupOrder":2,"groupName":"Multi-use Trails","groupBounds":[[-88.4961943075204,47.22764067200697],[-88.48670550309234,47.23521931273253]]}],"logo":"2025-07-31T10-20-30-773-07:00_US-MI-STSki_logo_0.png","banner":"2025-07-31T10-19-38-850-07:00_US-MI-STFatbike_Alexis_0.jpg","lastGroomedClass":"twoWeeksAgo","lgc":{"14d":{"ts":"2026-05-02T01:16:40.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"7d":{"ts":"2026-05-02T01:16:40.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"4d":{"ts":"2026-05-02T01:16:40.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"36h":{"ts":"2026-05-02T01:16:40.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"24h":{"ts":"2026-05-02T01:16:40.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"12h":{"ts":"2026-05-02T01:16:40.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"}},"lgcTr":{"14d":