":"CA-YT-MooseMountainDawson","type":"grooming-report","content":{"en":"\u003Cp>We're happy to report that the ski trails are still in great shape thanks to the little bit of snow that has been keeping them soft. &nbsp;Perfect for either classic or skate in these temperatures. &nbsp;You just have to get over the slush in the parking area! &nbsp;This may be our last groom, get out and enjoy it while it lasts! &nbsp;Thanks to all our groomers this year - John Howland, Ludo Antoine, Francis Bouffard, Stephen Kirth and Alastair Findlay-Brook - we've had an awesome season. &nbsp;And thanks to you, our users for spreading the love!\u003C/p>"},"account":"6961a7ae1e5f222418d08e85","author":"KATTS","timestamp":"2026-04-23T15:44:25.446Z","images":["2026-04-23T08-47-42-426-07:00_CA-YT-MooseMountainDawson_0.jpg","2026-04-23T08-47-50-495-07:00_CA-YT-MooseMountainDawson_0.jpg","2026-04-23T08-47-57-008-07:00_CA-YT-MooseMountainDawson_0.jpg","2026-04-23T08-48-04-658-07:00_CA-YT-MooseMountainDawson_0.jpg"],"imagesMeta":[{"createdAt":"2026-04-23T15:47:56.458Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-23T15:47:56.458Z","name":"2026-04-23T08-47-42-426-07:00_CA-YT-MooseMountainDawson_0.jpg","description":"Cross Country Skiing at Dawson City Winter Trails","alt":"Dawson City Winter Trails","clubId":"CA-YT-MooseMountainDawson","caption":{"en":"","fr":"","de":""}},{"createdAt":"2026-04-23T15:47:59.259Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-23T15:47:59.259Z","name":"2026-04-23T08-47-50-495-07:00_CA-YT-MooseMountainDawson_0.jpg","description":"Cross Country Skiing at Dawson City Winter Trails","alt":"Dawson City Winter Trails","clubId":"CA-YT-MooseMountainDawson","caption":{"en":"","fr":"","de":""}},{"createdAt":"2026-04-23T15:48:02.933Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-23T15:48:02.933Z","name":"2026-04-23T08-47-57-008-07:00_CA-YT-MooseMountainDawson_0.jpg","description":"Cross Country Skiing at Dawson City Winter Trails","alt":"Dawson City Winter Trails","clubId":"CA-YT-MooseMountainDawson","caption":{"en":"","fr":"","de":""}},{"created