 (30 kms dog-friendly) set on a 7,000 hectare landscape, The Callaghan offers something for everyone. Whether you choose to skate, classic ski, snowshoe or ski tour, The Callaghan Base at Alexander Falls offers a welcoming and affordable place to start your day&rsquo;s adventure\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>.\u003C/span>\u003C/p>"},"descriptionDirections":{"en":"\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>ADDRESS:\u003C/strong>\u003Cbr>Callaghan Country Wilderness Adventures\u003Cbr>#1000 Callaghan Valley Road\u003Cbr>Whistler, BC V0N 1B0\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Our base facility, \u003Cspan>The Callaghan Base at Alexander Falls\u003C/span>, is nestled 8.5km up Callaghan Valley Rd, off Hwy 99.&nbsp; On the left side of the road you will see a big sign for 'The Callaghan'.&nbsp; Turn left&nbsp; here, in between the majestic Alexander Falls&nbsp; sightseeing platform and the entrance to Whistler Olympic Park. This is where all of our ski and snowshoe adventures begin. From here all of the more than 100 km of day use cross country ski and snowshoe trails (including Whistler Olympic Park) are accessible.&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n"},"region":"British Columbia","country":"Canada","regions":["SkiCallaghan"],"logo":"2024-10-07T12-27-59-497-06:00_BC-CallaghanCountry_logo.png","banner":"BC-CallaghanCountry-banner.jpg","lastGroomedClass":"twoWeeksAgo","lgc":{"14d":{"ts":"2026-04-16T23:19:00.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"7d":{"ts":"2026-04-16T23:19:00.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"4d":{"ts":"2026-04-16T23:19:00.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"36h":{"ts":"2026-04-16T23:19:00.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"24h":{"ts":"2026-04-16T23:19:00.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"12h":{"ts":"2026-04-16T23:19:00.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"}},"lgg":{"14d":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":23379.96,"percent":60.53}],"7d":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":23379.96,"percent":60.53}],"4d":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":23379.96,"percent":60.53}],"36h":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":23379.96,"percent":60.53}],"24h":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":23379.96,"percent":