railsUpdate":"2026-03-09T19:32:24.392Z","tempUnits":"C","timezoneUTC":"-4","reportLatest":{"updatedAt":"2026-04-14T11:44:50.179Z","clubId":"US-NH-Dartmouth","type":"grooming-report","content":{"en":"\u003Cp>\u003Cem>Wednesday morning 4am update: &nbsp;brief Ginzu groom. Several short gaps between residual snow sections confirm it's time to run and bike, in preparation for next winter!\u003C/em>\u003C/p>\n\n\u003Cp>Well, Hoppy skiers, looks like that's going to do it! On behalf of our team, whether or not you are gathering today with friends and family, we are so very thankful for our sustainers, members, guests, volunteers, athletes and partners who helped make this a fantastic ski season. Almost 120 days of nordic skiing right here in Hanover, days, nights and early mornings! It's been a real pleasure and we sincerely hope you feel the same.&nbsp;\u003Cbr />We will take some time now to reflect on the season and how we could have made your experience better this winter with hopes to serve you even better next season! &nbsp;It matters to us. If you have a few minutes please fill out our short \u003Cstrong>\u003Ca href=\"https://forms.gle/gBam7pYkMJb5fnBG6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">OHOC End of Season Survey (click). \u003C/a>\u003C/strong>If you haven't already your feedback helps structure our offseason projects. We appreciate your help!\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Thank you skiers again for a great winter.&nbsp;\u003Cbr />See you on the bikes.&nbsp;\u003C/p>"},"account":"673627a8c82073d0c8939248","author":"Kor DuRoy","timestamp":"2026-04-05T11:20:30.000Z","deviceId":"9F49F201-38C4-469A-AC0A-2EEDE5127D0F"}},{"clubId":"CA-BC-RevelstokeNordicSkiClub","season":"winter","activities":["nordic"],"countryId":"CA","regionId":"BC","permalink":"Revelstoke-Nordic-Ski-Club","bounds":[[-118.25379820356149,50.93116528610887],[-118.21230098701014,50.97228103928927]],"offlineMapsBounds":[[[[-118.25951032186401,50.96012041182467],[-118.25950951650819,50.96012041182467],[-118.259509