"snow24h":1,"currentTemp":-4,"currentCond":"Excellent Conditions, -4 Variable clouds with a trace of snow possible","elevation":1599,"lastTrailsUpdate":"2026-01-17T17:42:09.736Z","tempUnits":"C","timezoneUTC":"-7","reportLatest":{"updatedAt":"2026-04-07T16:04:31.185Z","clubId":"BC-Silverstar","type":"grooming-report","content":{"en":"\u003Cp data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"13\">Good morning,\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp data-start=\"15\" data-end=\"281\">As we wrap up our final day of Nordic operations, we want to extend a thank you to all of our guests for being part of such a fantastic season. Your energy, passion, and support are what make the Nordic experience here at SilverStar Mountain truly special.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp data-start=\"283\" data-end=\"369\">We hope you&rsquo;ve enjoyed your time on the trails as much as we&rsquo;ve enjoyed welcoming you.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp data-start=\"371\" data-end=\"515\">We look forward to seeing you again for the 2026/2027 season. Until then, have a wonderful summer&mdash;and we hope to see you out on the bike trails.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp data-start=\"517\" data-end=\"560\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Warm regards,\u003Cbr data-start=\"530\" data-end=\"533\">Your Nordic Operations Team\u003C/p>"},"account":"6594c0e50f5b4000e06576d7","author":"Norman","timestamp":"2026-04-06T13:31:28.379Z"},"reportNotices":[{"updatedAt":"2026-07-11T15:49:56.748Z","clubId":"BC-Silverstar","type":"grooming-report-notice","content":{"en":"\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>NOTICE:\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Good monring, we had a mechanical breakdown on our groomer last night out on Alder Point last night. Our mechanics are on scene to assess and repair the situation. The map indicates a limited number of upper trails groomed while the lower trails are yet to be done. Please refer to the grooming report for todays groomed trails.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Apologizes for any inconvenience. Your Nordic Operations Team.\u003C/p>"},"account":"6594c0e50f5b4000e06576d7","author":"Norman","timestamp":"2026-02-07T14:14:40.390Z"},{"updatedAt":"2026-07-11T15:49:56.748Z","clubId":"BC-Silverstar","type":"grooming-report-notice","content":{"en":"\u003Cp>\u003Cem>\u003Cstrong>PLEASE NOTE,\u003C/strong>\u003C/em>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>We have had a mechanical breakdown of our Nordic Groomer this morning. Our mechanics are out diagnosing the problem. The SnowCat is parked on the trail at Captik Cabin.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The only trails groomed today are the ones you see on the map. As soon as the groomer is up and running again we will get as much groomed as time will allow.&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Please be aware non of the lower trails have been groomed at this time. Sorry for the inconvenience.\u003C/p>\n"},"account":"6594c0e50f5b4000e06576d7","author":"Norman","timestamp":"2026-03-04T14:59:34.028Z"},{"updatedAt":"2026-07-11T15:49:56.748Z","clubId":"BC-Silverstar","type":"grooming-report-notice","content":{"en":"\u003Cp>8am Update: The Nordic Groomer has been repaired and the team is currently grooming on the lower trail network. Please refer to the map for current grooming status. Total grooming of lower trails will be limited today.\u003C/p>"},"account":"67127cd225a84a1232e5769c","author":"Ian","timestamp":"2026-03-04T16:11:17.239Z"},{"updatedAt":"2026-07-11T15:49:56.748Z","clubId":"BC-Silverstar","type":"grooming-report-notice","content":{"en":"\u003Cp data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"16\">\u003Cstrong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"16\">PLEASE NOTE:\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp data-start=\"18\" data-end=\"250\">With the \u003Cspan>Sovereign to SilverStar Ski Marathon\u003C/span> just around the corner, we would like to inform our Nordic community that SilverStar&rsquo;s Upper Nordic Trail Network will be temporarily closed to support event preparation and operations.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp data-start=\"252\" data-end=\"270\">\u003Cstrong data-start=\"252\" data-end=\"270\">Closure Dates:\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul data-start=\"271\" data-end=\"332\">\n\u003Cli data-section-id=\"u9tj4g\" data-start=\"271\" data-end=\"290\">Friday, April 3\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli data-section-id=\"1v0z557\" data-start=\"291\" data-end=\"312\">Saturday, April 4\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli data-section-id=\"cu29ib\" data-start=\"313\" data-end=\"332\">Sunday, April 5\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp data-start=\"334\" data-end=\"443\">The Upper Trails will reopen to the public on \u003Cstrong data-start=\"380\" data-end=\"399\">Monday, April 6\u003C/strong>, our final day of operation for the season.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp data-start=\"445\" data-end=\"546\">Please note that \u003Cstrong data-start=\"462\" data-end=\"522\">SilverStar&rsquo;s Lower Nordic Trail Network will remain OPEN\u003C/strong> throughout this period.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp data-start=\"548\" data-end=\"628\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Thank you for your understanding and cooperation as we host this exciting event.\u003C/p>"},"account":"6594c0e50f5b4000e06576d7","author":"Norman","timestamp":"2026-03-30T14:37:55.153Z"},{"updatedAt":"2026-07-11T15:49:56.748Z","clubId":"BC-Silverstar","type":"grooming-report-notice","content":{"en":"\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>PLEASE NOTE:\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>With the&nbsp;Sovereign to SilverStar Ski Marathon&nbsp;just around the corner, we would like to inform our Nordic community that SilverStar&rsquo;s Upper Nordic Trail Network will be temporarily closed to support event preparation and operations.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Closure Dates:\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>Friday, April 3\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Saturday, April 4\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Sunday, April 5\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>The Upper Trails will reopen to the public on&nbsp;\u003Cstrong>Monday, April 6\u003C/strong>, our final day of operation for the season.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Please note that&nbsp;\u003Cstrong>SilverStar&rsquo;s Lower Nordic Trail Network will remain OPEN\u003C/strong>&nbsp;throughout this period.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Lower Trail\u003C/strong> system \u003Cstrong>access \u003C/strong>can be had at the \u003Cstrong>Village\u003C/strong> or \u003Cstrong>below the load station on the Silver Queen Chairlift.\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Thank you for your understanding and cooperation as we host this exciting event.\u003C/p>"},"account":"6594c0e50f5b4000e06576d7","author":"Norman","timestamp":"2026-04-02T13:58:53.933Z"},{"updatedAt":"2026-07-11T15:49:56.748Z","clubId":"BC-Silverstar","type":"grooming-report-notice","content":{"en":"\u003Cp data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"75\">Thank you for a fantastic season and for being part of our trail community.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp data-start=\"77\" data-end=\"269\">Please note that all trails are now officially closed for the 2025&ndash;2026 winter season. We kindly ask that everyone respects the closure to allow for spring conditions and seasonal maintenance.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp data-start=\"271\" data-end=\"412\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">We look forward to seeing you on the mountain bike trails this summer, and we can&rsquo;t wait to welcome you back for the 2026&ndash;2027 winter season.\u003C/p>"},"account":"6594c0e50f5b4000e06576d7","author":"Norman","timestamp":"2026-04-07T15:58:55.017Z"}]},{"clubId":"SK-LaRongeNutPoint","activities":["nordic"],"countryId":"CA","regionId":"SK","permalink":"La-Ronge-Nut-Point","bounds":[[-105.25360970835868,55.114508669513455],[-105.23730469841203,55.121956710238244]],"offlineMapsBounds":[[[[-105.26109613216082,55.110902445137555],[-105.24439921680695,55.110902445137555],[-105.24439921680695,55.11091114513748],[-105.24193175831475,55.11091114513748],[-105.24193175831475,55.111360145133254],[-105.23709945353137,55.111360145133254],[-105.23709945353137,55.111970045127514],[-105.23709893463236,55.111970045127514],[-105.23709893463236,55.11329124511508],[-105.23429873463236,55.11329124511508],[-105.23429873463236,55.11366894511153],[-105.23274077881901,55.11366894511153],[-105.232740