. See map for further information. There are a few small parking areas at some trailheads as indicated on the map with further information on the website.\u003C/p>"},"descriptionDirections":{"en":"\u003Cp>See website \u003Ca href=\"http://www.owwt.ca\">www.owwt.ca \u003C/a>for more information on \"getting there\" and parking options. However, if you look at the map, you will see how you may get there. Access is fairly easy via the Queensway if driving but beware of construction on Corkstown and the Magic of Lights show that may make it difficult to access via Corkstown.\u003C/p>"},"region":"Ontario","country":"Canada","regions":["OttawaUrbanWinter"],"logo":"ON-KanataNordic.png","banner":"ON-OttawaWest-banner.jpg","lastGroomedClass":"twoWeeksAgo","lgc":{"14d":{"ts":"2026-03-22T16:40:17.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"7d":{"ts":"2026-03-22T16:40:17.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"4d":{"ts":"2026-03-22T16:40:17.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"36h":{"ts":"2026-03-22T16:40:17.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"24h":{"ts":"2026-03-22T16:40:17.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"12h":{"ts":"2026-03-22T16:40:17.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"}},"lgg":{"14d":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":25999.11,"percent":98.48}],"7d":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":25999.11,"percent":98.48}],"4d":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":25999.11,"percent":98.48}],"36h":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":25999.11,"percent":98.48}],"24h":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":25999.11,"percent":98.48}],"12h":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":25999.11,"percent":98.48}]},"lastGroomedGroups":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":519.69,"percent":1.97}],"active":true,"timezone":"America/Toronto","liveTrack":true,"coordinates":[45.340747,-75.870853],"distance":26400.33058936997,"distanceGroups":[{"id":"novice","distance":6.64,"percent":25.150065502998466},{"id":"easy","distance":19.76,"percent":74.84993449700154}],"links":{"website":{"en":"https://www.owwt.ca/"},"weather":{"en":"https://www.theweathernetwork.com/ca/weather/ontario/kanata"}},"sponsor":true,"s