 Bike Birkie, and the Birkie Trail Run, the trails are maintained by our world-class Birkie Trail Staff and are open to the public year-round.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The newest addition to the American Birkebeiner Trail System,&nbsp;\u003Cstrong>\u003Ca href=\"https://www.birkie.com/mtv/\">Mt. Telemark Village\u003C/a>\u003C/strong>, is home to the Tormondsen Family Snowmaking Loops, Trek Mountain Biking Trails Powered by OTM, and kilometers of year-round trail systems!\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The non-profit 501(c)(3) American Birkebeiner Ski Foundation maintains 100% of the trail system.&nbsp;\u003Cstrong>\u003Ca href=\"https://www.birkie.com/give/donate/\">Learn about donating to support the trails here\u003C/a>\u003C/strong>.\u003C/p>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>"},"region":"Wisconsin","country":"United States","groups":[{"groupId":"MountTelemarkVillage","groupName":"Mount Telemark Village","groupBounds":[[-91.29522790909225,46.144183872290625],[-91.24370490433836,46.1944422130053]]},{"groupId":"OO","groupOrder":1,"groupName":"00","groupBounds":[[-91.34602797389331,46.05766747231279],[-91.28001982773472,46.15534241301536]]},{"groupId":"HatcheryCreek","groupOrder":2,"groupName":"Hatchery Creek","groupBounds":[[-91.48759634776707,46.005352472326166],[-91.34343596779796,46.060151713039744]]},{"groupId":"BirkieCourse","groupOrder":3,"groupName":"Birkie Courses","groupBounds":[[-91.48759634776707,46.005352472326166],[-91.25454540433836,46.1944422130053]]}],"logo":"US-WI-Birkie.png","banner":"US-WI-Birkie-banner.jpg","lastGroomedClass":"twoWeeksAgo","lgc":{"14d":{"ts":"2026-03-22T14:13:41.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"7d":{"ts":"2026-03-22T14:13:41.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"4d":{"ts":"2026-03-22T14:13:41.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"36h":{"ts":"2026-03-22T14:13:41.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"24h":{"ts":"2026-03-22T14:13:41.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"12h":{"ts":"2026-03-22T14:13:41.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"}},"lgg":{"14d":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":113842.38,"percent":99.84}],"7d":[{"