niche in natural food wholesales which led them to create a seasonal business that would allow customers to buy large quantities of the freshest, new crop nuts and dried fruit on the market. To this day, Rancho Vignola sells most of our products through annual wholesale orders, but also offers non-wholesale purchases at community Harvest Sales in November and online sales from December to July.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Richard and Sue not only built a successful and sustainable business model&mdash;they have created a community of people who are as passionate about quality food as they are.\u003C/p>"},"region":"British Columbia","country":"Canada","regions":["Okanagan"],"logo":"BC-LarchHills.png","lastGroomedClass":"twoWeeksAgo","lgc":{"14d":{"ts":"2026-03-17T17:39:56.186Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"7d":{"ts":"2026-03-17T17:39:56.186Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"4d":{"ts":"2026-03-17T17:39:56.186Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"36h":{"ts":"2026-03-17T17:39:56.186Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"24h":{"ts":"2026-03-17T17:39:56.186Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"12h":{"ts":"2026-03-17T17:39:56.186Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"}},"lgg":{"14d":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":53287.71,"percent":85.83}],"7d":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":53287.71,"percent":85.83}],"4d":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":53287.71,"percent":85.83}],"36h":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":53287.71,"percent":85.83}],"24h":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":53287.71,"percent":85.83}],"12h":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":53287.71,"percent":85.83}]},"lastGroomedGroups":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":8116.35,"percent":13.07}],"active":true,"timezone":"America/Vancouver","liveTrack":true,"coordinates":[50.7524655,-119.1789058],"distance":62086.63513829993,"distanceGroups":[{"id":"easy","distance":15.46,"percent":24.908536538981238},{"id":"intermediate","distance":38.87,"percent":62.61342091394041},{"id":"advanced","distance":7.75,"percent":12.478042547078312}],"links":{"website":{"en":"https://skilarchhills.ca/"},"weather":{"en":"https://skilarchhills.c