"US","regionId":"MT","permalink":"Seeley-Creek","bounds":[[-113.50269927374435,47.18621780401802],[-113.45497108645797,47.215870512737716]],"offlineMapsBounds":[[[[-113.50799326195829,47.19338270767],[-113.50692796757869,47.19338270767],[-113.50692796757869,47.19102170768575],[-113.50134923351811,47.19102170768575],[-113.50134923351811,47.189946407692915],[-113.49485642018162,47.189946407692915],[-113.49485642018162,47.188235107704315],[-113.4906788329134,47.188235107704315],[-113.4906788329134,47.185930507719696],[-113.48544089112481,47.185930507719696],[-113.48544089112481,47.184792907727285],[-113.47918959070438,47.184792907727285],[-113.47918959070438,47.1827193667411],[-113.47829678986743,47.1827193667411],[-113.47829678986743,47.18269660174125],[-113.47735796936362,47.18269660174125],[-113.47735796936362,47.18262033974175],[-113.46342884468271,47.18262033974175],[-113.46342884468271,47.1828870974074],[-113.4622853291079,47.1828870974074],[-113.4622853291079,47.183587480731866],[-113.4622852606391,47.183587480731866],[-113.4622852606391,47.18470515606923],[-113.45943335935,47.18470515606923],[-113.45943335935,47.18510249660894],[-113.45857222404688,47.18510249660894],[-113.45857222404688,47.18844960770291],[-113.45796291980405,47.18844960770291],[-113.45796291980405,47.20038920762327],[-113.45709466054029,47.20038920762327],[-113.45709466054029,47.20184430761356],[-113.45403101422215,47.20184430761356],[-113.45403101422215,47.20620280758449],[-113.44967458317146,47.20620280758449],[-113.44967458317146,47.21946761115165],[-113.47250186107694,47.21946761115165],[-113.47250186107694,47.215196011180176],[-113.48344851849559,47.215196011180176],[-113.48344851849559,47.21472351118332],[-113.49453436729179,47.21472351118332],[-113.49453436729179,47.214002911188125],[-113.49833608509648,47.214002911188125],[-113.49833608509648,47.21138101120564],[-113.49984188478973,47.21138101120564],[-113.49984188478973,47.210618811210715],[-113.4998419607588,47.210618811210715],[-113.4998419607588,47.209227611219994],[-113.50162641956162,47.209227611219994],[-113.50162641956162,47.20604541124124],[-113.50212114796277,47.20604541124124],[-113.50212114796277,47.20547131124507],[-113.50799326195829,47.20547131124507],[-113.50799326195829,47.19338270767]]]],"lastGroomed":"2026-03-16T22:14:23.000Z","weatherSources":["680907e6e3004a71b66ca4ee"],"name":{"en":"Seeley Creek Nordic Ski Trails"},"city":{"en":"Seeley Lake"},"groomedBy":{"en":"Seeley Lake Nordic Ski Club"},"sponsorText":{"en":"\u003Cp>Join us for a weekend or a night.&nbsp; Stay in a cabin on the lake or a room in the lodge.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>It's a winter thing!&nbsp; Drop in for appetizers and cocktails Wed-Sat from 4:30pm to 6:00pm.&nbsp; We continue to serve dinner by reservation Wed-Sat 5pm-8pm.&nbsp;\u003C/p>"},"description":{"en":"\u003Cp>\u003CspanArial',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0in; padding: 0in; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\">The USFS Seeley Creek Nordic Ski Trails, groomed by the Seeley Lake Nordic Ski Club, offer a well-balanced 26 kilometer blend of relaxed, rolling beginner and intermediate terrain, mixed with steeper, sinuous, more challenging expert trails. The ski trails at Seeley Creek offer something for everyone\u003Cspan>\u003Cins cite=\"mailto:Laurie%20Shammel\" datetime=\"2023-11-27T17:55\">,\u003C/ins>\u003C/span> from families with small kids, to seniors, to the most demanding cross-country ski racers.&nbsp;\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003CspanArial',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0in; padding: 0in; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\">Our grooming equipment has evolved over time. In the recent past, we used a fleet of state-of-the-art snowmobiles pulling \u003C/span>\u003Cspan>rollers, drags, or Ginzu&rsquo;s, depending on conditions. In 2021 our wildest dream was realized when a PistenBully 100 was made available to the club. The owner-operator of this machine has grooming experience at the highest levels of cross-country ski racing and his expertise, combined with the club&rsquo;s 30-year grooming history, means that trail conditions at Seeley Creek will be among the best you will find in Montana. If we get a foot and a half of snow overnight, we can now have it in shape for both skating and classic that morning. If conditions are settled, we park the PB 100 and fire up a couple of snowmobiles pulling Ginzu&rsquo;s.\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003CspanArial',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0in; padding: 0in; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\">Most of SLNSC\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>&rsquo;s volunteer groomers are also dedicated skiers who\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003Cins cite=\"mailto:Laurie%20Shammel\" datetime=\"2023-11-27T17:57\">,\u003C/ins>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan> over the years\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003Cins cite=\"mailto:Laurie%20Shammel\" datetime=\"2023-11-27T17:58\">,\u003C/ins>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan> have grown to be perfectionists when it comes to trail grooming. Consequently, we won&rsquo;t settle for less and you can expect to find the best grooming possible for any given snow condition.\u003C/span>\u003C/p>"},"region":"Montana","country":"USA","regions":["US-CCSAA","US-MT-WesternMontana"],"groups":[{"groupId":"AreaX","groupName":"Area X","groupBounds":[[-113.47389693174438,47.18621780401802],[-113.46566715855515,47.19186979324654]]},{"groupId":"MainTrailSystem","groupOrder":1,"groupName":"Main Trail System","groupBounds":[[-113.50269932571929,47.18830262035883],[-113.4632573065474,47.20563051274044]]},{"groupId":"Addition","groupOrder":2,"groupName":"Addition","groupBounds":[[-113.49454732598718,47.20034237201426],[-113.45497108645797,47.215870512737716]]}],"logo":"