 8.0/10.0, considering our trail base that is \"just enough.\" &nbsp;It should be reasonably firm and consistent for skate and tracks are set in the Campground, to the Dam, Blue Creek Meadow, and Prune Creek - where feasible for classic and double poling ! &nbsp;&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>It'll be a winter wonderland up there for at least a few days and the morning skiing will be fantastic 👍&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>You never know, which is really kinda nice, that this could be it. &nbsp;So go enjoy some really good spring skiing. &nbsp;Why go somewhere \"warm\" for spring break?! &nbsp;You're tough as nails. &nbsp;Or are you just cheap and stubborn. &nbsp;Either way, enjoy the trails while they last! &nbsp;\u003C/p>"},"account":"692f34aedd42915ab023ba12","author":"G-Money","timestamp":"2026-03-16T02:36:41.000Z","images":["2026-03-15T20-53-41-294-06:00_US-WY-BlackMountain_G-Money.jpg","2026-03-15T20-54-07-501-06:00_US-WY-BlackMountain_G-Money.jpg"],"deviceId":"004CE083-D55B-4D0B-ABFC-632CFA9C1705","imagesMeta":[{"createdAt":"2026-03-16T02:55:20.013Z","updatedAt":"2026-03-16T02:55:20.013Z","name":"2026-03-15T20-53-41-294-06:00_US-WY-BlackMountain_G-Money.jpg","description":"Black Mountain Nordic Daily Grooming Report","alt":"Black Mountain Nordic Daily Grooming Report","clubId":"US-WY-BlackMountain","caption":{"en":"","fr":"","de":""}},{"createdAt":"2026-03-16T02:55:19.705Z","updatedAt":"2026-03-16T02:55:19.705Z","name":"2026-03-15T20-54-07-501-06:00_US-WY-BlackMountain_G-Money.jpg","description":"Black Mountain Nordic Daily Grooming Report","alt":"Black Mountain Nordic Daily Grooming Report","clubId":"US-WY-BlackMountain","caption":{"en":"","fr":"","de":""}}]}},{"clubId":"US-WY-Turpin-Meadow","activities":["nordic"],"countryId":"US","regionId":"WY","permalink":"Turpin-Meadow","bounds":[[-110.2811211,43.8470484],[-110.2586016,43.8660543]],"lastGroomed":"2026-03-15T17:55:54.306Z","weatherSources":["680907e6e3004a71b66ca3a2"],"name":{"en":"Turpin Meadow Ranch"},"city":{"e