etiquette signs.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>We specifically request that hikers (without snowshoes), snowmobilers, ATV-ers, snow-bikers and fat bikers respect the intended ski use of our trail system and find other areas to recreate.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>BCNC DOG POLICY: Dog tracks and dog &ldquo;dirt&rdquo; damage the groomed trail surface. PlEASE respect the intended use of and considerable expense invested in the BCNC Nordic trails. Thank you!\u003C/p>"},"region":"Montana","country":"USA","regions":["US-MT-NorthShoreNordic"],"logo":"2025-08-20T09-37-20-351-07:00_US-MT-Bigfork_logo_0.png","banner":"2025-08-19T16-58-43-761-07:00_US-MT-Bigfork_0.jpg","lastGroomedClass":"twoWeeksAgo","lgc":{"14d":{"ts":"2026-03-15T17:16:15.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"7d":{"ts":"2026-03-15T17:16:15.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"4d":{"ts":"2026-03-15T17:16:15.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"36h":{"ts":"2026-03-15T17:16:15.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"24h":{"ts":"2026-03-15T17:16:15.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"12h":{"ts":"2026-03-15T17:16:15.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"}},"lgg":{"14d":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":11086.17,"percent":100}],"7d":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":11086.17,"percent":100}],"4d":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":11086.17,"percent":100}],"36h":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":11086.17,"percent":100}],"24h":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":11086.17,"percent":100}],"12h":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":11086.17,"percent":100}]},"active":true,"timezone":"US/Mountain","liveTrack":true,"coordinates":[48.141102,-114.008089],"distance":11086.169454507211,"distanceGroups":[{"id":"easy","distance":6.58,"percent":59.36757356120824},{"id":"intermediate","distance":3.18,"percent":28.703449485084935},{"id":"advanced","distance":1.32,"percent":11.928976953706814}],"links":{"website":{"en":"https://northshorenordic.org/bigfork-community-nordic-center/#"},"weather":{"en":"https://weather.com/weather/tenday/l/Bigfork+MT+59911:4:US"}},"snowDepth":5,"snowDepthUnpacked":12,"snow24h":14,"currentTemp":-5,"currentCond":"fresh snow","waxKick":"blue","waxGlide":"blue in the morning","elevation":945,"lastTrailsUpdate":"2025-12-02T17:53:48.325Z","tempUnits":"C","timezoneUTC":"-6","reportLatest":{"updatedAt":"2026-03-15T14:39:28.705Z","clubId":"US-MT-Bigfork","type":"grooming-report","content":{"en":"\u003Cp>23 degrees out and about 5-6\" of snow in the last day or so. We rolled the trails yesterday and brought the ginzu out last night. Trails will be skiable today..skating won't be the best but doable. Classic and Touring skiing may be a bit better. We made just one pass down the middle of the trails on the upper loops for touring. Come and get it as this will be the last few days of groomed/snowy trails this year. What a year...everyone's homework this summer is to come up with new and improved snow dances for next winter! Enjoy the last few days...\u003C/p>"},"account":"691e72aee6afa13673382b9e","author":"Aaron J","timestamp":"2026-03-15T14:35:09.978Z","snowDepth":5,"snowDepthUnpacked":12,"snow24h":14,"currentTemp":-5,"currentCond":"fresh snow","waxKick":"blue","waxGlide":"blue in the morning"}},{"clubId":"AB-CalgaryConfederationPark","activities":["nordic"],"countryId":"CA","regionId":"AB","permalink":"Calgary-Confederation","bounds":[[-114.1072574085267,51.07368597089745],[-114.09375642581769,51.082272711622366]],"offlineMapsBounds":[[[[-114.11307084807696,51.075660879687966],[-114.11298269499385,51.075660879687966],[-114.11298269499385,51.074024513001966],[-114.11128751593935,51.074024513001966],[-114.11128751593935,51.07273727971077],[-114.10739068005863,51.07273727971077],[-114.10739068005863,51.07263467971157],[-114.1071889505822,51.07263467971157],[-114.1071889505822,51.07008847973144],[-114.08917471263027,51.07008847973144],[-114.08917471263027,51.071849579717714],[-114.08802985430995,51.071849579717714],[-114.08802985430995,51.084048483278245],[-114.08837265033486,51.084048483278245],[-114.08837265033486,51.08407417158246],[-114.08878596189489,51.08407417158246],[-114