ing hills to more challenging intermediate and back country trails. Over 50% of the network is rated easy to provide interesting and exciting skiing for novice skiers as well as the entire family.\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>These trails connect Intervale, Kearsarge, and North Conway, a classic New England village offering outstanding scenery with views of the Saco River and magnificent Mt. Washington.&nbsp;\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cspan>Make time to visit the trailside businesses which include an Organic Distillery offering tours and tastings, an Organic Market and Cafe serving breakfast, lunch and snacks, an outdoor outfitter with their own label and full line of clothing and accessories to make your day more enjoyable, and an indoor golf facility with five simulators! Yes, you can ski and play some of the world's best courses in the same day! Visit our&nbsp;\u003Cstrong>website \u003C/strong>to learn more about these businesses and their special offers.&nbsp;\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cspan>Through a unique municipal relationship with this non-profit foundation, the network is used by the local schools for their cross country ski program, training and races. In addition all Conway residents and non-resident taxpayers are eligible for a greatly reduced season pass for less than the cost of a daily trail pass ... it's like it's free!\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cblockquote>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cspan>\u003Cstrong>\u003Cspan>\u003Ca href=\"https://www.mwvskitouring.org/support.html\">SUPPORT US\u003C/a>\u003C/span>\u003C/strong> by purchasing a season pass, daily memberships, participation in our events or \u003Cstrong>\u003Ca href=\"https://www.mwvskitouring.org/support.html\">make a tax-deductible donation online\u003C/a>\u003C/strong>. Your support is needed to help us continue to achieve our goals.\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n\u003C/blockquote>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cspan>Read about our \u003Cstrong>\u003Ca href=\"https://www.mwvskitouring.org/newhampshirelodging.html\">area lodging\u003C/a>\u003C/strong> including many trailside properties offering\u003Cstrong> \u003Ca href=\"https://www.mwvskitouring.org/newhampshirelodging.html#free\">\u003Cspan>FREE Skiing and Snowshoeing\u003C/span>\u003C/a> \u003C/strong>\u003Cspan>and our\u003Cstrong> \u003Ca href=\"https://www.mwvskitouring.org/events.html\">events\u003C/a>\u003C/strong> including weekly guided snowshoe tours,\u003Cstrong> \u003C/strong>and our popular annual\u003C/span>\u003Cstrong> \u003Cspan>\u003Ca href=\"https://www.mwvskitouring.org/Chocolate-Festival.html\">\u003Cspan>Inn-to-Inn Chocolate Festival\u003C/span>\u003C/a> \u003C/span>\u003C/strong>\u003Cspan>also known as the \"Sweetest Day on the Trails\".\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n\u003C/td>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003C/tr>\n\u003Ctr>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003C/tr>\n\u003Ctr>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003C/tr>\n\u003Ctr>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003C/tr>\n\u003Ctr>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003C/tr>\n\u003Ctr>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003C/tr>\n\u003Ctr>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003C/tr>\n\u003Ctr>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003C/tr>\n\u003Ctr>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003C/tr>\n\u003Ctr>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003C/tr>\n\u003Ctr>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003C/tr>\n\u003Ctr>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003C/tr>\n\u003Ctr>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003C/tr>\n\u003Ctr>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003C/tr>\n\u003Ctr>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003C/tr>\n\u003Ctr>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003Ctd>&nbsp;\u003C/td>\n\u003C/tr>\n\u003Ctr>\u003C/tr>\