-0\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"true\">4:30pm Ski sprints and snow games for all ages (dependent on snow conditions)\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"dhdfa\" data-offset-key=\"8nce3-0-0\">\n\u003Cdiv data-offset-key=\"8nce3-0-0\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"true\">5:30pm Lasagna Dinner (with garlic bread, salads, desserts, GF options)!WHO: Local ski community (any of you who enjoy skiing off County Road or Cummings Street, at the old Elk's Club, or in Hubbard Park. )\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"dhdfa\" data-offset-key=\"8t7pd-0-0\">\n\u003Cdiv data-offset-key=\"8t7pd-0-0\">\u003Cspan data-offset-key=\"8t7pd-0-0\">&nbsp;\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"dhdfa\" data-offset-key=\"2ufob-0-0\">\n\u003Cdiv data-offset-key=\"2ufob-0-0\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"true\">WHY: To give thanks to all the volunteers and land owners who make this community resource available.\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"dhdfa\" data-offset-key=\"4mg4d-0-0\">\n\u003Cdiv data-offset-key=\"4mg4d-0-0\">\u003Cspan data-offset-key=\"4mg4d-0-0\">&nbsp;\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"dhdfa\" data-offset-key=\"9v6bo-0-0\">\n\u003Cdiv data-offset-key=\"9v6bo-0-0\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"true\">HOW: Please register and pay in advance with this link:\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"dhdfa\" data-offset-key=\"8acsh-0-0\">\n\u003Cdiv data-offset-key=\"8acsh-0-0\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"true\">https://www.paypal.com/ncp/payment/N3CDFKABRE2SE\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"dhdfa\" data-offset-key=\"eu79d-0-0\">\n\u003Cdiv data-offset-key=\"eu79d-0-0\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"true\">This will let us plan food accordingly.\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"dhdfa\" data-offset-key=\"1dk26-0-0\">\n\u003Cdiv data-offset-key=\"1dk26-0-0\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"true\">$20 Adult, $40 Family, $10 Student.\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"dhdfa\" data-offset-key=\"al69f-0-0\">\n\u003Cdiv data-offset-key=\"al69f-0-0\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"true\">Limited day-of registration for an extra $5.\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"dhdfa\" data-offset-key=\"dqd2h-0-0\">\n\u003Cdiv data-offset-key=\"dqd2h-0-0\">\u003Cspan data-offset-key=\"dqd2h-0-0\">&nbsp;\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"dhdfa\" data-offset-key=\"69v3c-0-0\">\n\u003Cdiv data-offset-key=\"69v3c-0-0\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"true\">There will also be a fundraising raffle for continued support of local skiing. Prizes from Onion River Outdoors, Catamount Trail Association, Hunger Mountain Coop, Craftsbury Outdoor Center, Jasper Hill Cheese and More!\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"dhdfa\" data-offset-key=\"clppr-0-0\">\n\u003Cdiv data-offset-key=\"clppr-0-0\">\u003Cspan data-offset-key=\"clppr-0-0\">&nbsp;\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"dhdfa\" data-offset-key=\"192nj-0-0\">\n\u003Cdiv data-offset-key=\"192nj-0-0\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"true\">Call Nancy Chickering (802) 223-0577 with questions or to volunteer to help with serving, clean-up, or bringing gluten-free food options.\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>"},"account":"6712a0fdc3b2da0e067d76b5","author":"Alec","timestamp":"2026-03-13T12:36:28.082Z","images":["2026-03-13T08-37-59-895-04:00_US-VT-Montpelier_0.jpg"]}},{"clubId":"SK-MooseMountain","activities":["nordic","snowshoe"],"countryId":"CA","regionId":"SK","permalink":"Moose-Mountain","bounds":[[-102.41439974265431,49.82209477127776],[-102.29046549410904,49.88318821198726]],"lastGroomed":"2026-03-0