4],[-75.7347614049763,45.42271003861304],[-75.73491251458401,45.42271003861304],[-75.73491251458401,45.422743204196095],[-75.73835730339958,45.422743204196095],[-75.73835730339958,45.42360513720141],[-75.74246352061115,45.42360513720141],[-75.74246352061115,45.42379142275035],[-75.74278727045665,45.42379142275035],[-75.74278727045665,45.423895422749695],[-75.76288346373484,45.423895422749695],[-75.76288346373484,45.42173142276322],[-75.76990757167295,45.42173142276322],[-75.76990757167295,45.417680495287556],[-75.77032606825595,45.417680495287556],[-75.77032606825595,45.41746151490929],[-75.77292374613995,45.41746151490929],[-75.77292374613995,45.415403422802775],[-75.77586840568348,45.415403422802775],[-75.77586840568348,45.41240042282155],[-75.78180352750371,45.41240042282155],[-75.78180352750371,45.400030815268096]]]],"lastGroomed":"2026-02-21T16:11:57.000Z","weatherSources":["690f909aa7dfb36ea6a5eac8"],"name":{"en":"Sentier Blanc Val-Tétreau"},"city":{"en":"Gatineau"},"description":{"en":"\u003Cdiv>\u003Cstrong>The Sentier Blanc &ndash; Ski Along the River\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003C/strong>\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv>Discover&nbsp;\u003Cstrong>the Sentier Blanc\u003C/strong>, a unique cross-country skiing experience in the heart of the city. This&nbsp;\u003Cstrong>urban trail follows the majestic Ottawa River\u003C/strong>, offering every glide through a breathtaking winter landscape.\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv>Let yourself be carried by&nbsp;\u003Cstrong>the natural music of the flowing water\u003C/strong>, observe&nbsp;\u003Cstrong>the wildlife that thrives in winter\u003C/strong>, and enjoy&nbsp;\u003Cstrong>exceptional viewpoints\u003C/strong>&nbsp;along the snowy riverbanks.\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv>Accessible to everyone &mdash; from families to seasoned skiers &mdash; the Sentier Blanc stands out for&nbsp;\u003Cstrong>its gentle terrain\u003C/strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;\u003Cstrong>peaceful atmosphere\u003C/strong>, perfect for a relaxing outing, light training, or a quiet ski stroll.\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv>A place where city and nature meet &mdash; and every glide becomes a moment of calm.\u003C/div>","fr":"\u003Cdiv>\u003Cstrong>Le Sentier Blanc &ndash; Skier au fil de la rivi&egrave;re\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003C/strong>\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv>D&eacute;couvrez&nbsp;\u003Cstrong>le Sentier Blanc\u003C/strong>, une exp&eacute;rience unique de ski de fond au c&oelig;ur de la ville. Ce&nbsp;\u003Cstrong>sentier urbain longe la majestueuse rivi&egrave;re des Outaouais\u003C/strong>, offrant &agrave; chaque pas gliss&eacute; une immersion dans un paysage hivernal &agrave; couper le souffle.\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv>Laissez-vous porter par&nbsp;\u003Cstrong>la musique naturelle du courant\u003C/strong>, observez&nbsp;\u003Cstrong>la faune qui s&rsquo;&eacute;veille en hiver\u003C/strong>&nbsp;et profitez de&nbsp;\u003Cstrong>points de vue exceptionnels\u003C/strong>&nbsp;sur la rivi&egrave;re et ses berges enneig&eacute;es.\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv>Accessible &agrave; tous &mdash; des familles aux skieurs aguerris &mdash; le Sentier Blanc s&eacute;duit par&nbsp;\u003Cstrong>son faible d&eacute;nivel&eacute;\u003C/strong>&nbsp;et&nbsp;\u003Cstrong>son atmosph&egrave;re paisible\u003C/strong>, parfaite pour une sortie en plein air, un entra&icirc;nement l&eacute;ger ou une simple promenade sur skis.\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv>Un lieu o&ugrave; la nature et la ville se rencontrent&hellip; et o&ugrave; chaque glissade devient un moment de d&eacute;tente.\u003C/div>"},"descriptionDirections":{"en":"\u003Cdiv>\n\u003Cp>The parking lot at Parc Moussette is ideal for accessing it.\u003C/p>\n\u003C/div>","fr":"\u003Cp>Le stationnement du Parc Moussette est id&eacute;al pour y acc&eacute;der.\u003C/p>"},"region":"Quebec","country":"Canada","logo":"2025-11-09T17-31-24-211-08:00_CA-QC-SentierBlancValTétreau_0.jpg","lastGroomedClass":"twoWeeksAgo","lgc":{"14d":{"ts":"2026-02-21T16:11:57.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"7d":{"ts":"2026-02-21