e crew can get out and widen it sometime today for you skate skiiers.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>&nbsp;Enjoy the trails!\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>-Parker&nbsp;\u003C/p>"},"account":"6699459d05b6bb530516ea87","author":"Parker","timestamp":"2026-02-20T16:31:14.848Z"}},{"clubId":"US-MT-HomestakeLodge","activities":["nordic"],"countryId":"US","regionId":"MT","permalink":"Homestake-Lodge","bounds":[[-112.39984550050123,45.887605972356155],[-112.3683306383516,45.91171621307761]],"offlineMapsBounds":[[[[-112.40501455213229,45.896629216113574],[-112.40353649796684,45.896629216113574],[-112.40353649796684,45.895304182606104],[-112.40240501555394,45.895304182606104],[-112.40240501555394,45.89488514972902],[-112.40194945641993,45.89488514972902],[-112.40194945641993,45.890648916151605],[-112.40124209354771,45.890648916151605],[-112.40124209354771,45.885809116182344],[-112.38447228651377,45.885809116182344],[-112.38447228651377,45.8881633161674],[-112.3826058841734,45.8881633161674],[-112.3826058841734,45.88400851619381],[-112.3631620006067,45.88400851619381],[-112.3631620006067,45.89789481976124],[-112.36968445083657,45.89789481976124],[-112.36968445083657,45.90347811972573],[-112.37109721962854,45.90347811972573],[-112.37109721962854,45.906621419705736],[-112.37113349586456,45.906621419705736],[-112.37113349586456,45.909963319684486],[-112.37114547120358,45.909963319684486],[-112.37114547120358,45.910175119683146],[-112.37136473751839,45.910175119683146],[-112.37136473751839,45.910464419681304],[-112.37398016305785,45.910464419681304],[-112.37398016305785,45.913680119660825],[-112.3740230621844,45.913680119660825],[-112.3740230621844,45.91368761966079],[-112.3808076404851,45.91368761966079],[-112.3808076404851,45.91403516223175],[-112.38195017567003,45.91403516223175],[-112.38195017567003,45.91531331965045],[-112.3996924311934,45.91531331965045],[-112.3996924311934,45.908668919692715],[-112.40501455213229,45.908668919692715],[-112.40501455213229,45.896629216113574]]]],"lastGroomed":"2026-02-20T03:02:58.000Z","weatherSources":["680907e6e3004a71b66ca506"],"name":{"en":"Homestake Lodge"},"city":{"en":"Whitehall"},"sponsorText":{"en":"\u003Cp>HealthSource of Butte is your local source for high-quality chiropractic care and scientifically grounded healthcare information for you and your family. If you have unexplained neck pain, joint pain, or back pain, we'll help you find the source of the problem and get you relief. We also offer non-invasive treatment of bulging discs, sciatica, arthritis, and other conditions. We start by developing a treatment plan just for you&ndash;combining chiropractic care, Progressive Rehab, and overall wellness care to help you manage pain and get back to feeling like yourself. Our progressive rehab focuses on teaching you how to move, breaking down bad habits that may have contributed to whatever symptoms you are feeling now, and helps you learn excellent mechanics and new good habits to help stabilize your problem areas. We take a simple mechanical and biological approach to health: to be healthy we must move, eat and live in a means congruent with our natural design. When we step outside of the designs of nature, we suffer. It's time to return to health. We are the team to help you live how you are meant to live!\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The health of our bodies is the most important asset we have. Our bodies are the only thing we truly own from birth until death, so when we lose our health we become limited in our ability to do just about everything, causing a decline in our quality of life. We want you to be as active and healthy as you want to be without the limitations caused by pain, inflammation, and lack of mobility. Most people meet us wanting to be out of pain as soon as possible. We want to help you achieve that, and to remain out of pain and be even healthier 10 years from now!\u003C/p>"},"description":{"en":"\u003Cp>Homestake Lodge boasts exciting trails, grooming for skate skiing and classic, and has wonderful onsite lodging.&nbsp; We serve fresh, homemade food out of the Lodge on weekends.&nbsp; Rentals and lessons are available at anytime, please call ahead for lessons.&nbsp;\u003C/p>"},"descriptionDirections":{"en":"\u003Cp>Homestake Lodge is located just three miles off the I-90 Homestake Pass exit 233.&nbsp; GPS may be unreliable on certain applications and attempt to lead you over a jeep road that is closed in the winter.&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Be sure to take I-90 Exit 233.&nbsp; Head to the south side of I-90 and turn onto FS 240.&nbsp; This will be straigh off the exit ramp if coming from Butte. If coming from Bozeman, you will take a right off the exit ramp, cross over the insterstate.&nbsp; Do not drive toward Homestake Lake or Delmoe Lake.&nbsp; Before leaving the pavement, you will see a sign that say \"Homestake Lodge 3\" and \"Snowplowing Ends 3 Miles.\" After 3 miles, you will see a sign on your right that says \"Homestake Lodge\" and has an arrow to the right.&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>During the winter we plow the road from the Lodge to the Interstate whenever it snows several inches.&nbsp; The road is normally in good shape.&nbsp; Give us a call with any questions or issues.&nbsp; 406-522-3878\u003C/p>"},"region":"Montana","country":"USA","regions":["US-CCSAA"],"logo":"2023-11-28T13-08-20-079-08:00_US-MT-HomestakeLodge_logo.png","banner":"2023-11-28T13-08-37-760-08:00_US-MT-HomestakeLodge_Rob.jpg","lastGroomedClass":"twoWeeksAgo","lgc":{"14d":{"ts":"2026-02-20T03:02:58.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"7d":{"ts":"2026-02-20T03:02:58.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"4d":{"ts":"2026-02-20T03:02:58.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"36h":{"ts":"2026-02-20T03:02:58.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"24h":{"ts":"2026-02-20T03:02:58.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"12h":{"ts":"2026-02-20T03:02:58.000Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"}},"lgg":{"14d":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":224.26,"percent":0.82}],"7d":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":224.26,"percent":0.82}],"4d":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distance":224.26,"percent