orts in trail development and maintenance, snow grooming, snowshoe rentals, and advocacy of human-powered trails-based activities throughout Madison County.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Equipment and volunteers are made available to local organizations&ndash;&ndash;to assist in the expansion and usability of trail networks on public and private lands.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>FROSTY participates in the NYS DEC Volunteer Stewardship program, which enhances use of NYS public lands. As a registered 501(c)(3) 100% funded by donors, donations are invested in tools, equipment and supplies utilized exclusively on local trail networks.\u003C/p>"},"descriptionDirections":{"en":"\u003Cp>CPF Fairchild Hill: https://goo.gl/maps/us5w89ybyrAkfVsw5\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Meier's Creek Brewing: https://goo.gl/maps/qWgmH9SJMwJXUFuBA\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Lorenzo State Historic Site: https://goo.gl/maps/tke55pmDaakMzDPcA\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Madison County Distillery:&nbsp;https://goo.gl/maps/g4qxfZqMFcPEVJT17\u003C/p>"},"region":"New York","country":"USA","groups":[{"groupId":"FairchildHill","groupName":"CPF Fairchild Hill"},{"groupId":"MeiersCreekBrewingCo","groupName":"Meier's Creek Brewing Co."},{"groupId":"LorenzoState","groupName":"Lorenzo State Historic Site"},{"groupId":"CPFGorgeTrail","groupName":"CPF Gorge Trail"},{"groupId":"BurlingameTrails","groupName":"CPF Burlingame Trails"},{"groupId":"MadisonDistillery","groupName":"Madison County Distillery"}],"logo":"2023-07-14T10-17-16-093-07:00_US-NY-StoneyPond_logo.png","banner":"2023-07-21T10-54-25-505-04:00_US-NY-Frosty_Rob.jpg","lastGroomedClass":"twoWeeksAgo","lgc":{"14d":{"ts":"2026-02-14T20:23:39.408Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"7d":{"ts":"2026-02-14T20:23:39.408Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"4d":{"ts":"2026-02-14T20:23:39.408Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"36h":{"ts":"2026-02-14T20:23:39.408Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"24h":{"ts":"2026-02-14T20:23:39.408Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"},"12h":{"ts":"2026-02-14T20:23:39.408Z","cl":"twoWeeksAgo"}},"lgg":{"14d":[{"id":"twoWeeksAgo","distanc