main trailhead and three other cabins on the trails all have wood stoves and toilets. These cabins are easily accessed by both skiers and snowshoers.\u003C/p>"},"region":"British Columbia","country":"Canada","regions":["Okanagan"],"logo":"BC-KelownaNordic.png","banner":"BC-KelownaNordic-banner.jpg","lastGroomedClass":"twoWeeksAgo","active":true,"timezone":"America/Vancouver","liveTrack":true,"coordinates":[49.7792471,-119.17492],"distance":73128.3687090802,"distanceGroups":[{"id":"easy","distance":26.65,"percent":36.436069465570235},{"id":"intermediate","distance":39.39,"percent":53.867330878735785},{"id":"advanced","distance":7.09,"percent":9.696599655693918}],"links":{"website":{"en":"https://kelownanordic.com/"},"tickets":{"en":"https://www.kelownanordic.ca/membershiprates"},"email":{"en":"admin@kelownanordic.com  "},"fb":{"en":"https://www.facebook.com/kelownanordic"},"ig":{"en":"https://www.instagram.com/kelownanordic/"}},"currentCond":"Overcast","elevation":1259,"lastTrailsUpdate":"2026-03-17T16:44:03.750Z","tempUnits":"C","timezoneUTC":"-7","reportLatest":{"updatedAt":"2026-03-28T16:28:37.142Z","clubId":"BC-KelownaNordic","type":"grooming-report","content":{"en":"\u003Cp>Kelowna Nordic is closed for the 2025-2026 season.&nbsp; The last day of grooming was 16 March 2026, and since then we have seen daytime temperatures reaching into the mid-teens, accompanied by rapid snow melt.&nbsp; Skiing is not recommended.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Last fall considerable effort was put into widening most of the trails to (just) accommodate the new grooming machine.&nbsp; That work was done by many volunteers and will continue throughout the off-season, particularly in September and October.&nbsp; If you are able to help, please contact Mike at \u003Ca href=\"mailto:volunteer@kelownanordic.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">volunteer@kelownanordic.com.\u003C/a>&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>For other volunteer opportunities, see the\u003Cstrong> \u003C/strong>\u003Ca href=\"https: