vice&rsquo;s winter trail system provides endless miles of cross country skiing&mdash;both groomed and ungroomed&mdash;throughout the canyon. Most of the 30 km of groomed trails here are better suited to classic skiing. The grooming here is less frequent. The road into Hyalite is often icy and is plowed less frequently; for road conditions, check Friends of Hyalite social media posts.&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n"},"region":"Montana","country":"United States","regions":["US-MT-BSF","US-CCSAA"],"logo":"US-MT-ForestService.jpg","banner":"US-MT-BridgerSkiFoundation-Hyalite-banner.jpg","lastGroomedClass":"oneDayAgo","active":true,"timezone":"America/Boise","liveTrack":true,"coordinates":[45.489008,-110.980459],"distance":"36972.73850643855","distanceGroups":[{"id":"easy","distance":25.87,"percent":69.97142227046797},{"id":"intermediate","distance":11.1,"percent":30.028577729532035}],"links":{"website":{"en":"https://www.bridgerskifoundation.org/nordic/main"},"weather":{"en":"https://weather.com/weather/tenday/l/805f11fa1281c5343624ca798aafe975d24737294361c36fb6d1931454591b5f"},"tickets":{"en":"https://form-renderer-app.donorperfect.io/give/bridger-ski-foundation/25-26-trail-pass-sales"}},"elevation":2021,"lastTrailsUpdate":"2024-03-09T22:24:02.488Z","tempUnits":"F","timezoneUTC":"-6","reportLatest":{"updatedAt":"2026-03-27T01:42:31.128Z","clubId":"US-MT-BridgerSkiFoundation-Hyalite","type":"grooming-report","content":{"en":"\u003Cp>Thanks to the USFS for lending us the keys to Blackmore Castle this winter!!! We would not have had continuous skiiing without these fun, higher elevation loops. The Hyalite road will close to vehicle traffic on March 31st (All vehicles must be out by 6pm), and reopen May 15th. Happy Spring!\u003C/p>"},"account":"63937388624a86c6a246f89c","author":"BSF Trails ","timestamp":"2026-03-23T15:48:36.000Z"}},{"clubId":"US-MT-BridgerSkiFoundation-Sourdough","season":"winter","activities":["nordic"],"countryId":"US","regionId":"MT","permalink":"BSF-Sourdough","bounds":[[-111.0260511,45.524285],[-110.9186354,45.5919445]],"lastGroomed":"2026-03-07T22:24:32.032Z","weatherSources":["680907e5e3004a71b66ca222"],"name":{"en":"Sourdough"},"city":{"en":"Bozeman"},"groomedBy":{"en":"Groomed by: Bridger Ski Foundation"},"description":{"en":"\u003Cp dir=\"ltr\">Bozeman Creek (aka Sourdough Canyon) is a wide track that gradually climbs up the canyon, alongside Bozeman Creek on the national forest, with both classic and skate lanes. This is a popular multi-use trail, so expect to see lots of dogs, walkers, and skiers in the first few miles. Ski to Mystic Lake and back for 32 km (about 20 miles).&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp dir=\"ltr\">Parking: at the trailhead at the end of Sourdough Canyon Rd.&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n"},"region":"Montana","country":"United States","regions":["US-MT-BSF","US-CCSAA"],"logo":"US-MT-BridgerSkiFoundation.jpg","banner":"US-MT-BridgerSkiFoundation-Sourdough-banner.jpg","lastGroomedClass":"fourDaysAgo","active":true,"timezone":"America/Boise","liveTrack":true,"coordinates":[45.5667492,-111.009631],"distance":"24724.869221366298","distanceGroups":[{"id":"intermediate","distance":24.72,"percent":100}],"links":{"website":{"en":"https://www.bridgerskifoundation.org/nordic/main"},"weather":{"en":"https://weather.com/weather/tenday/l/805f11fa1281c5343624ca798aafe975d24737294361c36fb6d1931454591b5f"},"tickets":{"en":"https://form-renderer-app.donorperfect.io/give/bridger-ski-foundation/25-26-trail-pass-sales"}},"elevation":1702,"lastTrailsUpdate":"2024-01-09T23:09:11.549Z","tempUnits":"F","timezoneUTC":"-6","reportLatest":{"updatedAt":"2026-03-27T01:43:10.134Z","clubId":"US-MT-BridgerSkiFoundation-Sourdough","type":"grooming-report","content":{"en":"\u003Cp>Thank you to our friends at the USFS for their partnership in providing winter access to Sourdough and Hyalite!&nbsp;\u003C/p>"},"account":"63937388624a86c6a246f89c","author":"BSF Trails ","timestamp":"2026-03-22T16:30:44.000Z"}},{"clubId":"US-MT-BridgerSkiFoundation-SunsetHil