https://www.theweathernetwork.com/ca/weather/quebec/quebec","fr":"https://www.meteomedia.com/ca/meteo/quebec/plaines-dabraham"},"fb":{"en":"https://www.facebook.com/plainsabraham","fr":"https://www.facebook.com/plainesdabraham"},"ig":{"en":"https://www.instagram.com/plains_abraham/","fr":"https://www.instagram.com/plaines_dabraham/"}},"currentCond":"average\\correct","elevation":91,"lastTrailsUpdate":"2026-03-03T16:07:30.358Z","tempUnits":"C","timezoneUTC":"-4","reportLatest":{"updatedAt":"2026-03-19T14:17:00.254Z","clubId":"QC-PlainesAbraham","type":"grooming-report","content":{"en":"\u003Cp data-start=\"23\" data-end=\"57\">⚠️ \u003Cstrong data-start=\"26\" data-end=\"57\">Fin de saison - 19 mars 2026\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp data-start=\"59\" data-end=\"134\">La saison de ski de fond est maintenant termin&eacute;e sur les plaines d&rsquo;Abraham.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp data-start=\"136\" data-end=\"346\">La quantit&eacute; insuffisante de neige au sol, combin&eacute;e &agrave; une surface gazonn&eacute;e et largement glac&eacute;e sur l&rsquo;ensemble des pistes, rend la pratique du ski de fond non s&eacute;curitaire.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp data-start=\"348\" data-end=\"465\">Nous vous remercions pour cette belle saison et pour votre collaboration tout au long de l&rsquo;hiver. &Agrave; l&rsquo;an prochain! ⛷️\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp data-start=\"485\" data-end=\"528\">⚠️ \u003Cstrong data-start=\"488\" data-end=\"528\">End of Season &ndash; March 19, 2026\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp data-start=\"530\" data-end=\"607\">The cross-country ski season has now come to an end on the Plains of Abraham.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp data-start=\"609\" data-end=\"783\">Insufficient snow coverage, combined with grassy and heavily icy surfaces across all trails, makes cross-country skiing unsafe.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp data-start=\"785\" data-end=\"883\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Thank you for a great season and for your cooperation throughout the winter. Se