33415039628]]]],"lastGroomed":"2026-03-21T14:48:58.000Z","weatherSources":["680907e6e3004a71b66ca382"],"name":{"en":"Snow Mountain Ranch Nordic Center"},"city":{"en":"Winter Park"},"description":{"en":"\u003Cp>Welcome to the Nordic Center at YMCA of the Rockies &ndash; Snow Mountain Ranch.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Our world-class terrain meanders through pine forest, wide meadows, and all the way to the summit of Blue Ridge. To access our miles of trails for all ability levels and ages, including 6 miles open to fat tire bikes and dogs, you can purchase a day pass. &nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Members and overnight guests can choose from a variety of affordable lodging options and dozens of daily activities &mdash; plus, the whole family receives complimentary trail passes!\u003C/p>"},"region":"Colorado","country":"USA","regions":["US-CCSAA"],"groups":[{"groupId":"SnowRanchNordic","groupName":"Nordic Trails","groupBounds":[[-105.98044401961081,39.94993157372441],[-105.91303361888691,40.00591751444027]]},{"groupId":"SnowMtnRanchSnowshoe","groupOrder":1,"groupName":"Snowshoe Trails","groupBounds":[[-105.96890322490923,39.96772537372069],[-105.92657859077791,39.99010187594499]]}],"logo":"2022-12-24T15-09-18-034-08:00_US-CO-SnowMountainRanch_logo.png","banner":"2023-10-30T11-56-48-713-06:00_US-CO-SnowMountainRanch_Rob.jpg","lastGroomedClass":"oneDayAgo","active":true,"timezone":"America/Denver","liveTrack":true,"trackset":true,"tracksetType":"tracksetAuto","coordinates":[39.983591,-105.9279],"distance":97675.97118156844,"distanceGroups":[{"id":"easy","distance":27.13,"percent":27.773427296996246},{"id":"intermediate","distance":26.79,"percent":27.425718271447646},{"id":"advanced","distance":43.76,"percent":44.80085443155619}],"links":{"website":{"en":"https://ymcarockies.org/Nordic-Center"},"weather":{"en":"https://weather.com/weather/tenday/l/Winter+Park+Resort+CO+USCO0413:1:US"},"webcam":{"en":"https://ymcarockies.org/Portals/0/Webcams/snowmountainranchnordic/smrnordic.jpg"},"tickets":{"en":"https://www.ymcarockies.org/things-to-do/nordic-center"},"email":{"en":"info@ymcarockies.org"},"phone":{"en":"970-887-2152"},"fb":{"en":"https://www.facebook.com/ymcarockies/"},"ig":{"en":"https://www.instagram.com/ymcarockies/"},"tw":{"en":"https://x.com/YMCARockies"}},"currentTemp":-8.2,"elevation":2648,"lastTrailsUpdate":"2025-12-14T20:19:32.605Z","tempUnits":"F","timezoneUTC":"-6","reportLatest":{"updatedAt":"2026-03-22T15:26:08.937Z","clubId":"US-CO-SnowMountainRanch","type":"grooming-report","content":{"en":"\u003Cp>Good morning,\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Well it's a good thing we did the blue ridge summit party yesterday and thank you to everyone who made the trip up to the top.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>With the lowest recorded snowfall for a season in probably 50-80 years based on most reports in addition to one of the warmest winters on record plus the last week in the 60's &nbsp;toppped off by 72 degrees yesterday we made the call to throw in the towel and call it a season.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Yes there is still \"skiable snow up high\" but the access is getting to far and unsafe to provide a good experience.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>We are so thankful for all of your support and seeing you all out here skiing with us this season and let's keep those snow dances going all summer and hopefully have a little more snow to play with next year.&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>If you are already on your way over today hoping to ski or get those final strides in the only section of trail being prepared today is at the base of Gaskill/blue ridge to the gold mine in preparation for an annual gear test/review that you will see in cross county skier magazine later on. &nbsp;You will have to walk almost the entire way to that point if you are trying to get those last strides in.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Hope to see you all next year and we'll see you on the trials!&nbsp;\u003Cbr />\u003Cbr />\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Forgot to mention the ski shop will remain open for retail business normal hours 8:30am-5:00pm 7 days a week until April 5th Sunday so come on by to take advantage of end of season deals to get setup and ready for next year!&nbsp;\u003C/p>"},"account":"65d142f445d0a241b1125a98","author":"Shawn","timestamp":"2026-03-22T12:02:41.000Z","deviceId":"802EAB69-D09F-4C81-A369-42A66D7B621C"},"reportNotices":[{"updatedAt":"2026-07-11T15:49:56.507Z","clubId":"US-CO-SnowMountainRanch","type":"grooming-report-notice","content":{"en":"\u003Cp>Trail conditions update as of today.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Trails and conditions continue to change rapidly with the very warm temperatures so use extra caution and expect bare spots that you will need to stop and take your skis off for.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>We are done grooming the young's trails and today will be the last day for bald eagle as there are bare sections on the young's as well as the very steep section lower down on bald eagle.&nbsp;\u003Cbr />\u003Cbr />\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Use caution and enjoy the spring skiing&nbsp;\u003C/p>"},"account":"65d142f445d0a241b1125a98","author":"Shawn","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:37:48.000Z","deviceId":"802EAB69-D09F-4C81-A369-42A66D7B621C"}]},{"clubId":"US-WY-Shooting-Star","season":"winter","activities":["nordic"],"countryId":"US","regionId":"WY","permalink":"Shooting-Star-Nordic-Track","bounds":[[-110.8371565,43.5672974],[-110.8225304,43.5818015]],"lastGroomed":"2026-02-23T14:27:19.399Z","weatherSources":["680907e6e3004a71b66ca392"],"name":{"en":"Shooting Star Nordic Track"},"city":{"en":"Teton Village"},"description":{"en":"\u003Cp>Shooting Star's nordic facilities are available to \u003Cstrong>passholders only. \u003C/strong>Passes are available for purchase through the Shooting Star Nordic Center.&nbsp;\u003C/p>"},"region":"Wyoming","country":"USA","regions":["US-WY-JHNordic","US-CCSAA"],"logo":"2023-10-16T15-15-27-339-07:00_US-WY-JacksonTown_logo.png","banner":"2022-11-20T23-30-20-825-05:00_US-WY-Shooting-Star_Finn.jpg","lastGroomedClass":"oneDayAgo","active":true,"timezone":"America/Denver","liveTrack":true,"coordinates":[43.572344,-110.82777345],"distance":"11051.34957938882","distanceGroups":[{"id":"easy","distance":6.72,"percent":60.8389311079868},{"id":"intermediate","distance":4.33,"percent":39.1610688920132}],"links":{"website":{"en":"https://jhnordic.com/trails/shooting-star-nordic-track/"},"weather":{"en":"https://weather.com/weather/tenday/l/83025:4:US"}},"sponsor":true,"sponsorLogo":"2022-10-28T15-33-40-046-07:00_US-WY-JacksonTetonCounty_logo.png","sponsorLink":"https://nordic-pulse.com/ski-areas/US/WY/region/Jackson-Hole-Nordic","elevation":1913,"lastTrailsUpdate":"2024-01-13T20:29:16.125Z","tempUnits":"F","timezoneUTC":"-6","reportLatest":{"updatedAt":"2026-03-09T11:56:06.028Z","clubId":"US-WY-Shooting-Star","type":"grooming-report","content":{"en":"\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Nordic Course Closed \u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>March 9, 2026:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>This is likely our final Nordic Update for this season, as unseasonably warm temperatures continue to deteriorate our existing snowpack. Trails are to remain closed, and we&rsquo;ll continue to monitor conditions for one more week. If weather continues as is, we'll then shift our focus on snow removal to prepare the course for the upcoming golf season \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">beginning Monday, March 16\u003C/span>\u003Csup>\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">th\u003C/span>\u003C/sup>\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">.\u003C/span> Outlook is calling for mostly rain this week, followed by very warm temperatures around 60*F all next week. Thanks again for everyone&rsquo;s understanding during this unusual winter.\u003C/p>"},"account":"638a3c71981fbee04a3559f0","author":"tshrum@shootingstarjh.com","timestamp":"2026-03-09T11:53:41.000Z","deviceId":"89C2E503-CE53-4FEC-92FB-A28E3020FB73"}},{"clubId":"US-NV-MtRose","activities":["nordic"],"countryId":"US","regionId":"NV","permalink":"NevadaNordic-MtRose","bounds":[[-119.93552646909693,39.28291977386288],[-119.91248983151868,39.30096031817421]],"offlineMapsBounds":[[[[-119.94017364714631,39.2793223538576],[-119.9283180978568,39.2793223538576],[-119.9283180978568,39.27943185385704],[-119.92801028076681,39.27943185385704],[-119.92801028076681,39.27963785385598],[-119.92115472471706,39.27963785385598],[-119.92115472471706,39.28062046420261],[-119.91940135337622,39.28062046420261],[-119.91940135337622,39.28200590671829],[-119.91662051267939,39.28200590671829],[-119.91662051267939,39.28353575955869],[-119.91551998773531,39.28353575955869],[-119.91551998773531,39.28389479373416],[-119.90806872829832,39.28389479373416],[-119.90806872829832,39.28577825382443],[-119.90784158844731,39.28577825382443],[-119.90784158844731,39.29576945742876],[-119.90932717439821,39.29576945742876],[-119.90932717439821,39.299553221424006],[-119.90975992998948,39.299553221424006],[-119.90975992998948,39.30455746097102],[-119.9262635308568,39.30455746097102],[-119.9262635308568,39.30277435663838],[-119.92714106584997,39.30277435663838],[-119.92714106584997,39.30180185739774],[-119.93187058453219,39.30180185739774],[-119.93187058453219,39.29252896316815],[-119.93277414074947,39.29252896316815],[-119.93277414074947,39.29179507103732],[-119.93971097330878,39.29179507103732],[-119.93971097330878,39.288631057465466],[-119.93993695622643,39.288631057465466],[-119.93993695622643,39.28842505746653],[-119.94017364714631,39.28842505746653],[-119.94017364714631,39.2793223538576]]]],"lastGroomed":"2026-05-01T02:44:38.000Z","weatherSources":["680907e6e3004a71b66ca39e"],"name":{"en":"Nevada Nordic"},"city":{"en":"Incline Village"},"groomedBy":{"en":"Nevada Nordic"},"region":"Nevada","country":"USA","regions":["US-CCSAA"],"logo":"2023-06-08T15-28-42-937-06:00_US-NV-MtRose_logo.png","banner":"2022-11-13T21-34-16-479-07:00_US-NV-MtRose_Rob.jpg","lastGroomedClass":"today","active":true,"timezone":"America/Los_Angeles","liveTrack":true,"trackset":true,"tracksetType":"tracksetAuto","coordinates":[39.283973,-119.933948],"distance":21741.78956019025,"distanceGroups":[{"id":"easy","distance":10.29,"percent":47.30612517375123},{"id":"intermediate","distance":11.46,"percent":52.69387482624877}],"links":{"website":{"en":"https://nevadanordic.org/"},"weather":{"en":"https://forecast.weather.gov/MapClick.php?lat=39.2511&lon=-119.9669#.Y2b_EOzMIq0"}},"currentCond":"small moon ","waxKick":"blank","waxGlide":"blank","elevation":2486,"lastTrailsUpdate":"2025-05-19T21:20:08.102Z","tempUnits":"F","timezoneUTC":"-7","reportLatest":{"updatedAt":"2026-05-01T03:51:03.725Z","clubId":"US-NV-MtRose","type":"grooming-report","content":{"en":"\u003Cp>Well...it is over. Last groom, for realz. If you have a notion to ski, do it tomorrow. The results were good tonight. There is corduroy🤣😂. Kept it wide so skaters don't get their tips hung up in the chum on the shoulders. For those of you who want to continue skiing for a few weeks, consider off trail. Today my wife and I skated from 10 till one-ish. We did a lap on the groomed, then decided to dabble off piste. It was rockin'. The snow was solid with a thin creamy top layer. Lip smackin' good! We were able to skate to top of Lakeview, meander to Overlook, then putz around till we got down to the meadow. A lot of up and down woop-dee-doos and going around some bare spots. Probably not everyone would get their jollies this way but we found it fun. Clean snow, few tracks, new scenery, and a bunch of laughs. Well, anyway I can't wait to go skiing tomorrow!\u003C/p>"},"account":"692f34c7dd42915ab023bc97","author":"fredr","timestamp":"2026-05-01T03:11:24.000Z","deviceId":"C783B122-240D-44AC-91A2-EFB2D5CCFB9E"}},{"clubId":"US-WI-WinMan","season":"winter","activities":["nordic"],"countryId":"US","regionId":"WI","permalink":"WinMan-Trails","bounds":[[-89.8852336,46.1781367],[-89.8381689,46.1955137]],"lastGroomed":"2026-04-07T13:47:09.000Z","weatherSources":["680907e6e3004a71b66ca3a6"],"name":{"en":"WinMan Trails"},"city":{"en":"Winchester"},"region":"Wisconsin","country":"USA","banner":"2022-12-01T23-19-44-330-07:00_US-WI-WinMan_Rob.jpg","lastGroomedClass":"oneDayAgo","active":true,"timezone":"America/Winnipeg","liveTrack":true,"trackset":true,"tracksetType":"tracksetChecked","coordinates":[46.186799,-89.884227],"distance":"21868.151964160872","distanceGroups":[{"id":"easy","distance":7.45,"percent":34.059148869570215},{"id":"intermediate","distance":10.55,"percent":48.243469020244866},{"id":"advanced","distance":3.87,"percent":17.69738211018492}],"links":{"website":{"en":"https://www.winmantrails.com/ski/"},"weather":{"en":"https://weather.com/weather/tenday/l/Winchester+WI?canonicalCityId=6a6ca6c08f44d91557e899f28730b01e3f0b3360075f86547c6ca921a4e4438d"},"email":{"en":"info@winmantrails.com"},"fb":{"en":"https://www.facebook.com/WinManTrails"}},"currentTemp":-5.9,"currentCond":"Snowing","elevation":506,"lastTrailsUpdate":"2023-11-07T18:56:27.377Z","tempUnits":"F","timezoneUTC":"-5","reportLatest":{"updatedAt":"2026-04-10T11:30:36.328Z","clubId":"US-WI-WinMan","type":"grooming-report","content":{"en":"\u003Cp data-start=\"526\" data-end=\"648\">\u003Cstrong>CLOSED FOR THE SEASON&nbsp;❌\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong data-olk-copy-source=\"MessageBody\">After 131 days of skiing\u003C/strong>, we must finally say goodbye to the season.&nbsp;The trails are now officially closed for the season\u003Cstrong>&nbsp;\u003C/strong>so we can turn our efforts and attention to the summer.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Thank you all for making it the most memorable in our history.&nbsp;\u003C/p>"},"account":"6367425449db9eb8ff784db0","author":"Isaac","timestamp":"2026-04-10T11:30:18.703Z"}},{"clubId":"US-WY-TrailCreek","activities":["nordic"],"countryId":"US","regionId":"WY","permalink":"Trail-Creek-Nordic","bounds":[[-110.91092828409533,43.484527772942116],[-110.8861302473012,43.5024844136655]],"offlineMapsBounds":[[[[-110.91588614169473,43.483759830824475],[-110.91242859996755,43.483759830824475],[-110.91242859996755,43.48237823083255],[-110.9119402743029,43.48237823083255],[-110.9119402743029,43.48115313083972],[-110.90093785145002,43.48115313083972],[-110.90093785145002,43.480930330841026],[-110.886332339657,43.480930330841026],[-110.886332339657,43.4899594307882],[-110.88117097778316,43.4899594307882],[-110.88117097778316,43.49434893076251],[-110.88117062694505,43.49434893076251],[-110.88117062694505,43.504525134358666],[-110.88166396710359,43.504525134358666],[-110.88166396710359,43.50608153434955],[-110.89757052574042,43.50608153434955],[-110.89757052574042,43.50490643435643],[-110.90122900018162,43.50490643435643],[-110.90122900018162,43.50386553436253],[-110.90125577302184,43.50386553436253],[-110.90125577302184,43.503778034363044],[-110.90179722314997,43.503778034363044],[-110.90179722314997,43.503619790839565],[-110.90288500170072,43.503619790839565],[-110.90288500170072,43.50315543436669],[-110.90425952314997,43.50315543436669],[-110.90425952314997,43.4985751343935],[-110.90689287107902,43.4985751343935],[-110.90689287107902,43.49644643440594],[-110.91440847168435,43.49644643440594],[-110.91440847168435,43.49527893441277],[-110.91588614169473,43.49527893441277],[-110.91588614169473,43.483759830824475]]]],"lastGroomed":"2026-03-17T16:39:11.113Z","weatherSources":["680907e6e3004a71b66ca3b2"],"name":{"en":"Trail Creek Nordic"},"city":{"en":"Wilson"},"region":"Wyoming","country":"USA","regions":["US-WY-JHNordic","US-CCSAA"],"logo":"2023-10-16T15-15-27-333-07:00_US-WY-JacksonTown_logo.png","banner":"2022-11-10T21-18-32-528-07:00_US-WY-Shooting-Star_Rob.jpg","lastGroomedClass":"twoWeeksAgo","active":true,"timezone":"America/Edmonton","liveTrack":true,"coordinates":[43.499735,-110.894339],"distance":18828.763293185482,"distanceGroups":[{"id":"easy","distance":10.37,"percent":55.081456342640244},{"id":"intermediate","distance":5.17,"percent":27.456044499668465},{"id":"advanced","distance":3.29,"percent":17.462499157691248}],"links":{"website":{"en":"https://jhskiclub.org/trail-creek"},"weather":{"en":"https://weather.com/weather/tenday/l/Wilson+WY?canonicalCityId=e9a398cdea0d7f60c7f331bd42cd021fbb22c0108546bcea06885e69974a22b4"}},"sponsor":true,"sponsorLogo":"2022-10-28T15-33-40-046-07:00_US-WY-JacksonTetonCounty_logo.png","sponsorLink":"https://nordic-pulse.com/ski-areas/US/WY/region/Jackson-Hole-Nordic","elevation":1944,"lastTrailsUpdate":"2026-01-08T00:47:22.797Z","tempUnits":"F","timezoneUTC":"-6","reportLatest":{"updatedAt":"2026-04-05T17:23:54.994Z","clubId":"US-WY-TrailCreek","type":"grooming-report","content":{"en":"\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>\u003Cspan>Trail Creek Grooming Report\u003C/span>\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>&nbsp;\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/strong>\u003Cstrong>\u003Cspan>Final Edition!\u003C/span>\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>\u003Cspan>Let&rsquo;s Pause a Little Longer&hellip;\u003C/span>\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cspan>&nbsp;\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Well, it looks like we&rsquo;ll have to pause a little longer&mdash;perhaps only until November 15th, if we&rsquo;re lucky. It has certainly been a season for the record books, marked by excessive rain and unseasonably warm temperatures. On the bright side, we fared much better than many other Nordic areas in the West. We enjoyed several months of fantastic midwinter skiing, where consistent, cool temperatures provided the perfect recipe for lovely skiing. We even managed to host a couple of races that couldn&rsquo;t be held elsewhere.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cspan>&nbsp;\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Despite the challenging conditions, our JHSC programs were a roaring success. We saw record participation this year, with thousands of smiles logged by youth and adults alike in our little piece of Nordic paradise.\u003Cspan>&nbsp; \u003C/span>It is something of a miracle what can happen when you strap a pair of skinny skis on your feet in a place like ours, surrounded by lots of other amazing people.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cspan>&nbsp;\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Thanks so much to all the people who come together to keep this fantastic place we call Trail Creek providing so much joy to so many people!\u003Cspan>&nbsp; \u003C/span>We&rsquo;ll pause for a few months, and then do it all again.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cspan>&nbsp;\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Steve Swan\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The Groomer\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cspan>&nbsp;\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>PS A special thanks to Gannett Swan for his support to the grooming department.\u003C/p>\n"},"account":"6386dc9486b301f88304cba8","author":"Steve","timestamp":"2026-04-05T17:23:14.494Z","images":["2026-04-05T11-23-42-755-06:00_US-WY-TrailCreek_0.jpg","2026-04-05T11-23-50-389-06:00_US-WY-TrailCreek_0.jpg"],"imagesMeta":[{"createdAt":"2026-04-05T17:23:56.652Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-05T17:23:56.652Z","name":"2026-04-05T11-23-42-755-06:00_US-WY-TrailCreek_0.jpg","description":"Cross Country Skiing at Trail Creek Nordic","alt":"Trail Creek Nordic","clubId":"US-WY-TrailCreek","caption":{"en":"","fr":"","de":""}},{"createdAt":"2026-04-05T17:23:58.147Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-05T17:23:58.147Z","name":"2026-04-05T11-23-50-389-06:00_US-WY-TrailCreek_0.jpg","description":"Cross Country Skiing at Trail Creek Nordic","alt":"Trail Creek Nordic","clubId":"US-WY-TrailCreek","caption":{"en":"","fr":"","de":""}}]}},{"clubId":"US-WY-TetonReserve","activities":["nordic"],"countryId":"US","regionId":"ID","permalink":"Teton-Reserve-Nordic","bounds":[[-111.1101624,43.6257897],[-111.0879765,43.635553]],"lastGroomed":"2026-02-12T15:45:56.531Z","weatherSources":["680907e6e3004a71b66ca3c2"],"name":{"en":"Teton Reserve Nordic Trail"},"city":{"en":"Teton County"},"region":"Idaho","country":"USA","regions":["US-WY-JHNordic","US-CCSAA","US-WY-JHNordic-TetonValleyTrails"],"logo":"2023-04-04T21-53-25-289-07:00_US-WY-Driggs_logo.png","lastGroomedClass":"fourDaysAgo","active":true,"timezone":"America/Edmonton","liveTrack":true,"trackset":true,"tracksetType":"tracksetChecked","coordinates":[43.63128,-111.100239],"di