n strategic places to allow skiers to warm up and rest before starting the return loop.\u003C/p>","fr":"\u003Cp>&Agrave; 20 min de Qu&eacute;bec, les sentiers de pas classique en milieu forestier offrent une exp&eacute;rience unique. Les skieurs les plus exp&eacute;riment&eacute;s peuvent profiter d&rsquo;options longues distances jusqu&rsquo;au refuge la tani&egrave;re, une boucle de 25 km qui se trouve &agrave; 630 m. d&rsquo;altitude sur les terres du S&eacute;minaire de Qu&eacute;bec.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Les familles y trouvent leur compte avec une boucle facile le long de la rivi&egrave;re Waterloo offrant des options de retour de 3, 5 et 7 km jusqu&rsquo;au fameux refuge Poulin.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Notre r&eacute;seau compte 5 refuges chauff&eacute;s. Les refuges ont &eacute;t&eacute; construits dans des endroits strat&eacute;giques pour permettre aux skieurs de se r&eacute;chauffer et se reposer avant d&rsquo;entamer la boucle de retour.\u003C/p>"},"region":"Quebec","country":"Canada","logo":"2023-11-29T11-00-30-683-07:00_QC-SentiersDuMoulins_logo.png","banner":"2023-11-29T10-57-35-037-07:00_QC-SentiersDuMoulins_Raph.jpg","lastGroomedClass":"today","active":true,"timezone":"America/New_York","liveTrack":true,"coordinates":[46.98397156538032,-71.26730729428988],"distance":42801.90430457622,"distanceGroups":[{"id":"easy","distance":13.7,"percent":32.013311055096224},{"id":"intermediate","distance":5.87,"percent":13.70733097724286},{"id":"advanced","distance":23.23,"percent":54.27935796766094}],"links":{"website":{"en":"https://www.sentiersdumoulin.com/en/activity/cross-country-skiing/","fr":"https://www.sentiersdumoulin.com/activite/ski-de-fond/"},"weather":{"en":"https://www.yr.no/en/forecast/daily-table/46.984,-71.266","fr":"https://www.yr.no/en/forecast/daily-table/46.984,-71.266"},"tickets":{"en":"https://app.endorphine.ca/collaborator/9dd436c1-7779-447f-91a6-48936c65dec4?_gl=1*1hmag42*_ga*MTEyMTAzMTU0My4xNzYzOTMwMjg2*_ga_1SPPKQYXWS*czE3NjM5MzAyODUkbzEkZzEkdDE3