canoteurs! La pr&eacute;sence de 40 esp&egrave;ces de mammif&egrave;res, dont le loup, t&eacute;moigne du caract&egrave;re sauvage du territoire et de son immensit&eacute;. La via ferrata du Diable, une activit&eacute; interm&eacute;diaire entre la randonn&eacute;e et l'escalade, permet de d&eacute;couvrir tout autrement les montagnes de ce parc. De toute nature, le parc national du Mont-Tremblant est ouvert &agrave; l'ann&eacute;e.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Dans le secteur de la Diable, 55 km de pistes de ski de fond classique sont trac&eacute;s et entretenus m&eacute;caniquement. Les pistes sont r&eacute;parties en 5 parcours, class&eacute;es de facile &agrave; tr&egrave;s difficile. Il est possible d'effectuer un arr&ecirc;t dans l'un de nos 5 refuges pour casser la cro&ucirc;te ou vous r&eacute;chauffer.\u003C/p>"},"region":"Quebec","country":"Canada","logo":"2023-12-05T12-18-01-980-08:00_QC-ParcNationalDuMontTremblant_logo.png","banner":"2023-12-05T12-17-46-376-08:00_QC-ParcNationalDuMontTremblant_Rob.jpg","lastGroomedClass":"oneDayAgo","active":true,"timezone":"America/Toronto","liveTrack":true,"coordinates":[46.33189765,-74.49911345],"distance":58875.65470134185,"distanceGroups":[{"id":"easy","distance":30.75,"percent":52.23207297856442},{"id":"intermediate","distance":10.12,"percent":17.180662826013602},{"id":"advanced","distance":18.01,"percent":30.587264195421955}],"links":{"website":{"en":"https://www.sepaq.com/pq/mot/index.dot?language_id=1","fr":"https://www.sepaq.com/pq/mot/index.dot"},"weather":{"en":"https://weather.com/en-CA/weather/today/l/5275610d6ee0abac0d72a2fea61b2561b05833fb556921fedcc4e7f37424b8d6","fr":"https://weather.com/en-CA/weather/today/l/5275610d6ee0abac0d72a2fea61b2561b05833fb556921fedcc4e7f37424b8d6"}},"elevation":345,"lastTrailsUpdate":"2025-03-01T00:09:01.322Z","tempUnits":"C","timezoneUTC":"-4","reportLatest":{"updatedAt":"2026-03-09T13:16:32.256Z","clubId":"QC-ParcNationalDuMontTremblant","type":"grooming-report","content":{"en":"\u003Cp>End of the Cross-Country Ski Season &ndash; Parc national du Mont-Tremblant\u003Cbr>Dear visitors,\u003Cbr>The cross-country ski season at Parc national du Mont-Tremblant is now officially over. Equipment rentals and ski ticket sales are therefore closed for the season.\u003Cbr>You may still access our ski trails; however, please note that no further grooming or maintenance will be carried out. Trail conditions will vary depending on the weather, so we encourage all users to be cautious.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Experts trails are closed.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cbr>Our snowshoe trails remain open. Due to current conditions &mdash; very soft, wet, and fragile snow &mdash; snowshoes are mandatory to help protect the environment and support conservation efforts.\u003Cbr>The entire park team wishes to extend a heartfelt thank you to our loyal visitors for another wonderful season. Your presence and enthusiasm are what make our work so meaningful.\u003Cbr>We look forward to welcoming you back next season!\u003Cbr>&mdash; The Parc national du Mont-Tremblant Team\u003C/p>","fr":"\u003Cp>Fin de la saison de ski de fond &ndash; Parc national du Mont-Tremblant\u003Cbr>La saison de ski de fond est maintenant termin&eacute;e au Parc national du Mont-Tremblant. La location d&rsquo;&eacute;quipement ainsi que la vente de billets sont ferm&eacute;es pour le reste de la saison. Il demeure possible d&rsquo;explorer les sentiers de ski, mais ils ne seront plus entretenus. Les conditions pouvant varier rapidement, nous invitons les visiteurs &agrave; faire preuve de prudence lors de leurs sorties.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Les sentiers experts sont pr&eacute;sentement ferm&eacute;s.\u003Cbr>Les sentiers de raquette restent ouverts. En raison de la neige tr&egrave;s molle et d&eacute;tremp&eacute;e, le port de raquettes est obligatoire afin de prot&eacute;ger les milieux naturels et d&rsquo;assurer la conservation de nos &eacute;cosyst&egrave;mes.\u003Cbr>Nous remercions chaleureusement notre fid&egrave;le client&egrave;le pour cette belle saison pass&eacute;e &agrave; vos c&ocirc;t&eacute;s. Votre pr&eacute;sence et votre enthousiasme nous motivent chaque jour. Au plaisir de vous accueillir de nouveau l&rsquo;hiver prochain !\u003C/p>"},"account":"656f8933f2dd67cd01d4ba13","author":"Eric","timestamp":"2026-03-09T13:12:26.531Z"}},{"clubId":"FR-HD-HautSaugeaisBlanc","activities":["nordic"],"countryId":"FR","regionId":"FR-HD","permalink":"Haut-Saugeais-Blanc","bounds":[[6.446353716254356,46.948430972081155],[6.492725548123965,46.975405312801634]],"offlineMapsBounds":[[[[6.441084623935192,46.944833509319935],[6.459376612518795,46.944833509319935],[6.459376612518795,46.94751160930224],[6.464312267398489,46.94751160930224],[6.464312267398489,46.950029709285594],[6.466517466844629,46.950029709285594],[6.466517466844629,46.95028130928393],[6.479187425772826,46.95028130928393],[6.479187425772826,46.95422460925787],[6.487502832117365,46.95422460925787],[6.487502832117365,46.95700670923947],[6.492282719528431,46.95700670923947],[6.492282719528431,46.96069300921511],[6.496393774795984,46.96069300921511],[6.496393774795984,46.96604440917974],[6.497998063086583,46.96604440917974],[6.497998063086583,46.97802171275623],[6.49788457336687,46.97802171275623],[6.49788457336687,46.9789164127503],[6.49695448396747,46.9789164127503],[6.49695448396747,46.97900241274973],[6.481196733413421,46.97900241274973],[6.481196733413421,46.97811671275559],[6.468625071796532,46.97811671275559],[6.468625071796532,46.97313201278856],[6.462202299658847,46.97313201278856],[6.462202299658847,46.97165941279831],[6.449958378325608,46.97165941279831],[6.449958378325608,46.96747871282596],[6.4484501780796535,46.96747871282596],[6.4484501780796535,46.9644933128457],[6.442983770184054,46.9644933128457],[6.442983770184054,46.959951912875724],[6.442544090393311,46.959951912875724],[6.442544090393311,46.959787712876796],[6.442025545777082,46.959787712876796],[6.442025545777082,46.956504812898515],[6.441084623935192,46.956504812898515],[6.441084623935192,46.944833509319935]]]],"lastGroomed":"2025-03-03T04:07:14.867Z","weatherSources":["680907e6e3004a71b66ca522"],"name":{"en":"Le Haut Saugeais Blanc","fr":"Le Haut Saugeais Blanc"},"city":{"en":"Hauterive-la-Fresse","fr":"Hauterive-la-Fresse"},"description":{"en":"\u003Cp>Situ&eacute; dans le Haut-Doubs, en plein c&oelig;ur du Massif Jurassien, &agrave; une dizaine de kilom&egrave;tres de Pontarlier et &agrave; moins de 10min de Montbenoit, l'espace nordique du Haut Saugeais Blanc est le site donnant acc&egrave;s au r&eacute;seau GTJ (et &agrave; toutes les stations de ski de fond qui le constitue) le plus proche de Besan&ccedil;on sans avoir &agrave; traverser l'agglom&eacute;ration de Pontarlier.&nbsp;Nich&eacute; dans l'&eacute;crin du site de la Perdrix, le d&eacute;part des pistes est organis&eacute; autour du centre n&eacute;vralgique du domaine et si&egrave;ge de l'association : le g&icirc;te d'&eacute;tape du Haut Saugeais Blanc. Dot&eacute; d'un parking et de tous les services n&eacute;cessaires (location, redevances, h&eacute;bergement, restauration&hellip;), le g&icirc;te constitue le point de d&eacute;part de vos excursions &agrave; ski ou en raquettes.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cbr>Fort de 25km de pistes balis&eacute;es de ski de fond et de plusieurs itin&eacute;raires raquettes qui lui sont propres, le domaine nordique pr&eacute;sente diverses connexions avec le reste du r&eacute;seau nordique jurassien; &agrave; savoir une liaison avec le site de la Malmaison (Pontarlier) et une liaison GTJ (Grande Travers&eacute;e du Jura) permettant de rejoindre en un petit kilom&egrave;tre la Suisse et un vaste espace de ski desservant les sites du Val de Morteau (via Charopey, les Seignes), de la Vall&eacute;e de la Br&eacute;vine (CH) et du Larmont (Pontarlier) en passant par les pistes du r&eacute;seau suisse roman de ski de fond des Cernets (CH)\u003C/p>"},"region":"Haut-Doubs","country":"France","logo":"2023-12-06T19-