:26.33379161084054}],"links":{"website":{"en":"https://www.eastmannh.org/ski"},"weather":{"en":"https://www.yr.no/en/forecast/daily-table/43.504,-72.093"}},"snowDepth":3,"snow12h":17,"currentTemp":-6.9,"elevation":366,"lastTrailsUpdate":"2026-02-24T00:01:46.842Z","tempUnits":"F","timezoneUTC":"-4","reportLatest":{"updatedAt":"2026-03-06T16:36:55.265Z","clubId":"US-NH-Eastman","type":"grooming-report","content":{"en":"\u003Cp>All trails are groomed, track set in some areas(until the track setter broke), Craig's corridor and trail 8 are also groomed. Sledding hill is open and skating rink is closed. We will not be grooming again unless we get more snow, at that point we will groom Johns glen. We will close the golf course on Monday.&nbsp;\u003Cbr />Thanks for all the positive feedback on a great season. Billy, Dave, Doug, Matt, Kian and Bill\u003C/p>"},"account":"692f34bedd42915ab023bbc0","author":"Billy M","timestamp":"2026-03-06T16:29:54.000Z","deviceId":"1B4A96EB-3CB6-4D99-B529-57C3161BE459"}},{"clubId":"FR-HS-Megeve","activities":["nordic"],"countryId":"FR","regionId":"FR-HS","permalink":"Domaine-Nordique-Megeve","bounds":[[6.6329111,45.8176617],[6.6590791,45.8607126]],"lastGroomed":"2021-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","weatherSources":["680907e6e3004a71b66ca536"],"name":{"en":"Domaine Nordique de Megève","fr":"Domaine Nordique de Megève"},"city":{"en":"Megève","fr":"Megève"},"description":{"en":"\u003Cp>Experienced cross-country skiers, fans of the classic style or loyal skaters, all find themselves in the Nordic area of ​​Meg&egrave;ve. Perched on the heights of Meg&egrave;ve, the cross-country ski trails criss-cross between sunny plateaus, immaculate fields and snow-covered forests. Whether you like contemplative cross-country skiing, healthy cross-country skiing, playful cross-country skiing or sports cross-country skiing, you are bound to find the Nordic track of your dreams in Meg&egrave;ve.\u003C/p>","fr":"\u003Cp>Skieurs de fond chevronn&eacute;s, adeptes du style classique ou fid&egrave;les du skating, tous se retrouvent sur le domaine nordique de Meg&egrave;ve. Perch&eacute;es sur les hauteurs de Meg&egrave;ve, les pistes de ski de fond sillonnent entre plateaux ensoleill&eacute;s, champs immacul&eacute;s et for&ecirc;ts enneig&eacute;es. Alors que vous aimiez le ski de fond contemplatif, le ski de fond sant&eacute;, le ski de fond ludique ou le ski de fond sportif, vous trouverez forc&eacute;ment &agrave; Meg&egrave;ve la piste nordique de vos r&ecirc;ves.\u003C/p>"},"region":"Haute-Savoie","country":"France","groups":[{"groupId":"MegeveLivraz","groupName":"Site Nordique de La Livraz"},{"groupId":"MegeveMontArbois","groupName":"Secteur Mont d'Arbois"}],"logo":"2023-12-21T13-02-39-196-08:00_FR-HS-Megeve_logo.png","banner":"2023-12-21T13-01-37-654-08:00_FR-HS-Megeve_Rob.jpg","lastGroomedClass":"twoWeeksAgo","active":true,"timezone":"Europe/Paris","liveTrack":true,"coordinates":[45.836174296286444,6.643530197905277],"distance":"20122.67355382913","distanceGroups":[{"id":"easy","distance":2.27,"percent":11.289709664408363},{"id":"intermediate","distance":3.72,"percent":18.48257020139187},{"id":"advanced","distance":5.12,"percent":25.42368598862347}],"links":{"website":{"en":"https://www.megeve-tourisme.fr/en/sports-hiver/domaine-skiable/domaine-nordique/","fr":"https://www.megeve-tourisme.fr/sports-hiver/domaine-skiable/domaine-nordique/"},"weather":{"en":"https://www.yr.no/en/forecast/daily-table/45.836,6.644","fr":"https://www.yr.no/en/forecast/daily-table/45.836,6.644"},"webcam":{"en":"https://app.webcam-hd.com/megeve/la-livraz","fr":"https://app.webcam-hd.com/megeve/la-livraz"}},"snowDepth":15,"snowAnnual":30,"currentTemp":-1,"currentCond":"Neige douce","elevation":1378,"lastTrailsUpdate":"2024-01-09T16:49:03.184Z","tempUnits":"C","timezoneUTC":"2"},{"clubId":"US-CO-TellurideValleyFloor","activities":["nordic"],"countryId":"US","regionId":"CO","permalink":"Telluride-Valley-Floor","bounds":[[-107.871725,37.9389812],[-107.8212914,37.950729]],"lastGroomed":"2026-02-22T19:59:48.153Z","weatherSources":["680907e6e3004a71b66ca53e"],"name":{"en":"Town of Telluride Valley Floor"},"nameS":{"en":"Valley Floor"},"city":{"en":"Telluride"},"groomedBy":{"en":"Rollo Nordic Trail Grooming"},"description":{"en":"\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Nordic\u003C/strong> skiers of all abilities are offered more than 15 kilometers of rolling, open terrain on the Town of Telluride Valley Floor Preserve. There is nearly 10 kilometers of trail specially groomed for snow bikes, hiking, snow shoeing, and skiing.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Dogs\u003C/strong> are NOT allowed on any Valley Floor Preserve Nordic or multi-use trails. Dogs are allowed on Boomerang Road Trail and parts of the River Trail.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Grooming\u003C/strong> of Valley Floor trails occurs between dawn and dusk. Please be aware of equipment operations and yield to groomers at all times.\u003C/p>"},"descriptionDirections":{"en":"\u003Cp>There are three main trailheads. From east to west, these are Mahoney, Boomerang, and Lawson.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Parking\u003C/strong> is available on Mahoney Drive, or parking is available at Carhenge skier lot, just one block away. Limited parking available at Boomerang Road trailhead. Ample parking available at Lawson Hill.\u003C/p>"},"region":"Colorado","country":"USA","regions":["US-CO-Telluride-Regional-Trails"],"logo":"2025-01-24T14-35-15-162-08:00_US-CO-TellurideValleyFloor_logo_0.png","banner":"2025-01-09T17-22-02-419-07:00_US-CO-TellurideValleyFloor_Rob_0.jpg","lastGroomedClass":"twoWeeksAgo","active":true,"timezone":"America/Denver","liveTrack":true,"coordinates":[37.939004,-107.821714],"distance":25056.6677082854,"distanceGroups":[{"id":"easy","distance":25.06,"percent":100}],"links":{"website":{"en":"https://www.telluridenordic.com/nordic-trails/"},"weather":{"en":"https://www.yr.no/en/forecast/daily-table/37.934,-107.805"}},"currentTemp":-9.9,"elevation":2661,"lastTrailsUpd