2b1675fe7e8c84dcebbbf3"],"name":{"en":"Lost Lake Nordic Trails"},"city":{"en":"Whistler"},"groomedBy":{"en":"Resort Municipality of Whistler"},"description":{"en":"\u003Cp>Only steps from Whistler Village, venture into a winter wonderland at Lost Lake Nordic Trails. Explore 25km of pristinely groomed trails suitable for all ages and abilities, plus 15km of dedicated snowshoe paths, or enjoy 4km of illuminated trails - the only night skiing near Whistler Village. At Lost Lake PassivHaus, you&rsquo;ll find everything you need for your Nordic adventure: rentals, lessons, the Connection Caf&eacute;, and a cozy day lodge to relax and recharge. Out on the trails, the lakeside warming hut offers a rustic spot to take a break&mdash;just remember to bring your own treats!\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Hours: 8 a.m. to 8 p.m. daily\u003Cem>* (except Holidays)\u003C/em>\u003C/p>"},"descriptionDirections":{"en":"\u003Cp>\u003Ca href=\"https://maps.app.goo.gl/zFZVBrZBTeVenG3VA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Main Entrance - Lost Lake PassivHaus (Tickets, Rentals and Daylodge)\u003C/a>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Ca href=\"https://maps.app.goo.gl/ABuG3bpCjRu3dFug7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">North Entrance - Nicklaus North parking lot (Tickets)\u003C/a>\u003C/p>"},"region":"British Columbia","country":"Canada","regions":["US-CCSAA"],"groups":[{"groupId":"LostLakeCore","groupName":"Lost Lake Core Ski Trails","groupBounds":[[-122.94964636964029,50.11902927118934],[-122.93254069082518,50.14425411190937]]},{"groupId":"ChateauSkiTrails","groupOrder":1,"groupName":"Chateau Ski Trails","groupBounds":[[-122.9468880564598,50.118579371189476],[-122.9260776308158,50.13948191191079]]},{"groupId":"NicklausNorth","groupOrder":2,"groupName":"Nicklaus North","groupBounds":[[-122.96517389951516,50.13369627118493],[-122.94242489082518,50.14425411190937]]},{"groupId":"LostLakeSnowshoe","groupOrder":3,"groupName":"Snowshoe Trails","groupBounds":[[-122.94936876809342,50.11897647118935],[-122.93192234384