er Happy Hour, live music &amp; appetizers for passholders, members + Retail Blowout sale &amp; live music\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Cafe and Bar will still be open\u003C/strong> for lunch from 11AM-3PM, and Apres 3-5PM Daily. The cafe crew can let you into the wax room and locker room during these hours if you need.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>The Retail Store\u003C/strong> will be open Sat/ Sun March &nbsp;28/29 from 11am-3pm with deep discounts on what's left! Wax room and Locker room will be open on those days too.\u003C/p>"},"account":"6615bdd714526e588a1e5793","author":"Sally","timestamp":"2026-03-17T00:15:17.000Z"},"reportNotices":[{"updatedAt":"2026-07-11T15:49:56.803Z","clubId":"US-CA-TahoeDonner","type":"grooming-report-notice","content":{"en":"\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>2026-27 SEASON PASSES\u003C/strong> are currently on sale at the discounted Spring Price - see the website for details.\u003C/p>"},"account":"6615bdd714526e588a1e5793","author":"Sally","timestamp":"2026-03-14T13:08:30.003Z"},{"updatedAt":"2026-07-11T15:49:56.803Z","clubId":"US-CA-TahoeDonner","type":"grooming-report-notice","content":{"en":"\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>The Alder Creek Cafe will remain OPEN f\u003C/strong>or lunch 11-3 &amp; Apres / Happy Hour from 3-5pm daily.&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Two more winter Edi Bol's on Mondays 5-7pm\u003C/p>"},"account":"6615bdd714526e588a1e5793","author":"Sally","timestamp":"2026-03-14T13:05:24.921Z"}]},{"clubId":"US-OR-Bachelor","season":"winter","activities":["nordic"],"countryId":"US","regionId":"OR","permalink":"Mt-Bachelor-Nordic-Center","bounds":[[-121.72179949707362,43.99974597282053],[-121.66682880709193,44.018522413543636]],"offlineMapsBounds":[[[[-121.72679990639062,43.996148527801424],[-121.69812152818486,43.996148527801424],[-121.69812152818486,43.99782002779146],[-121.6923632324798,43.99782002779146],[-121.6923632324798,44.00178752776785],[-121.69067250806016,44.00178752776785],[-121.69067250806016,44.000606773774926],[-121.68457751299324,44.000606773774926],[-121.68457751299324,44.000395708678],[-121.67585087034972,44.000395708678],[-121.67585087034972,43.999603427780855],[-121.66182732631347,43.999603427780855],[-121.66182732631347,44.010073131374234],[-121.66295267108721,44.010073131374234],[-121.66295267108721,44.01059703137113],[-121.66358689063276,44.01059703137113],[-121.66358689063276,44.011360231366574],[-121.66477136446294,44.011360231366574],[-121.66477136446294,44.01255703135945],[-121.66525346749673,44.01255703135945],[-121.66525346749673,44.0133819173546],[-121.66942504858604,44.0133819173546],[-121.66942504858604,44.01365613135291],[-121.66975064025789,44.01365613135291],[-121.66975064025789,44.01600184542443],[-121.67421281849708,44.01600184542443],[-121.67421281849708,44.019441833318524],[-121.6742657014582,44.019441833318524],[-121.6742657014582,44.01979303131636],[-121.6842826560781,44.01979303131636],[-121.6842826560781,44.0221195313025],[-121.70110958994871,44.0221195313025],[-121.70110958994871,44.020799031310375],[-121.70541085408598,44.020799031310375],[-121.70541085408598,44.019387931318775],[-121.7060653763415,44.019387931318775],[-121.7060653763415,44.017949648316744],[-121.70902532298842,44.017949648316744],[-121.70902532298842,44.015739131340496],[-121.71184291462426,44.015739131340496],[-121.71184291462426,44.013849631351746],[-121.72679990639062,44.013849631351746],[-121.72679990639062,43.996148527801424]]]],"lastGroomed":"2026-04-19T14:04:52.000Z","weatherSources":["680907e6e3004a71b66ca5ba"],"name":{"en":"Mt. Bachelor Nordic Center"},"nameS":{"en":"Mt. Bachelor"},"city":{"en":"Bend"},"description":{"en":"\u003Cp>With 56 km of groomed trails for classic and skate skiing, 10 km of signed and packed snowshoe trails, a full rental service, a variety of xc ski lessons and multi-week clinic opportunities, the Nordic Center offers something for everyone! Enjoy shopping at the onsite retail store, dining at the deliciously healthy Nordic Cafe, and warming up by the cozy wood stove after a day on the trails.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Plan all your winter adventures right from our website with your pre-purchase of trail passes, rentals, and lessons for speedy and simple trail access. Enjoy the nation&rsquo;s longest groomed Nordic season and beauty of the great outdoors at your own pace. Adventure guaranteed!\u003C/p>"},"region":"Oregon","country":"USA","banner":"2024-10-03T14-04-30-858-06:00_US-OR-Bachelor_Rob.jpg","lastGroomedClass":"twoWeeksAgo","active":true,"timezone":"America/Los_Angeles","liveTrack":true,"coordinates":[44.003221891184396,-121.67625498727408],"distance":43445.96405270795,"distanceGroups":[{"id":"easy","distance":11.2,"percent":25.784183298535662},{"id":"intermediate","distance":20.55,"percent":47.303985242781124},{"id":"advanced","distance":11.69,"percent":26.911831458683167}],"links":{"website":{"en":"https://www.mtbachelor.com/plan-your-trip/nordic/overview"},"weather":{"en":"https://www.yr.no/en/forecast/daily-table/44.003,-121.679"}},"elevation":1941,"lastTrailsUpdate":"2026-04-13T15:25:11.494Z","tempUnits":"F","timezoneUTC":"-7","reportLatest":{"updatedAt":"2026-04-20T21:30:20.648Z","clubId":"US-OR-Bachelor","type":"grooming-report","content":{"en":"\u003Cp>Mt Bachelor Nordic is now closed for the 25/26 ski season. The trails are \"uncontrolled and unpatrolled\". In the event of an emergency, contact 911. And note that access to the mountain will be completely restricted on the following dates: 4/22, 4/26- 4/29, 5/3-5/6.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Thank you to all of the wonderful passholders and guests who joined us on the trails this winter; we can't wait to see you again next season! In the meantime, please contact the Nordic Lodge at 541-693-0999 for questions &amp; pass sales.&nbsp;\u003C/p>"},"account":"663a5f0197b78a9b6c794ae9","author":"Sydney","timestamp":"2026-04-20T21:17:15.973Z","images":["2026-04-20T14-23-34-149-07:00_US-OR-Bachelor_0.jpg"],"imagesMeta":[{"createdAt":"2026-04-20T21:28:56.586Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-20T21:30:19.108Z","name":"2026-04-20T14-23-34-149-07:00_US-OR-Bachelor_0.jpg","description":"Cross Country Skiing at Mt. Bachelor Nordic Center","alt":"Mt. Bachelor Nordic Center","clubId":"US-OR-Bachelor","caption":{"en":"","fr":"","de":""}}]}},{"clubId":"US-WA-Leavenworth","activities":["fatbike","nordic"],"countryId":"US","regionId":"WA","permalink":"Leavenworth-Ski-Hill","bounds":[[-120.67192372320186,47.61231453084193],[-120.65347840553122,47.61919671262921]],"weatherSources":["680907e6e3004a71b66ca5c6"],"name":{"en":"Leavenworth Ski Hill"},"city":{"en":"Leavenworth"},"groomedBy":{"en":"Leavenworth Winter Sports Club"},"description":{"en":"\u003Cp>The Leavenworth Winter Sports Club maintains 26km of tracks and skating lanes that offer a variety of skiing terrain across three areas around Leavenworth. Each location offers a slightly different experience both in scenery and terrain.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The&nbsp;\u003Ca href=\"https://skileavenworth.com/locations/winter-locations/icicle-river\">\u003Cspan>Icicle River Trails\u003C/span>\u003C/a> are our beginner-friendly location with excellent scenery being tucked away at the mouth of the incredible Icicle Canyon. This is the default Nordic Lesson location.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Our&nbsp;\u003Ca href=\"https://skileavenworth.com/locations/winter-locations/golf-course\">\u003Cspan>Golf Course\u003C/span>\u003C/a> trail network boasts intermediate terrain tucked along the scenic Wenatchee River. Wide sweeping curves lead through open groves of huge pines while surrounded by gorgeous views of the Cascades and home to numerous deer that share the trails.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cspan>\u003Ca href=\"https://skileavenworth.com/locations/winter-locations/ski-hill\">Ski Hill\u003C/a>\u003C/span> is not only home to our alpine operations but also our more advanced Nordic trail system. These trails loop through beautiful forests and end back at the historic Ski Hill Lodge - the perfect place for apr&egrave;s-ski. This location also offers five kilometers of lighted Nordic skiing until 10pm every night during winter operations.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The&nbsp;\u003Ca href=\"https://skileavenworth.com/locations/winter-locations/peshastin-mill-site\">\u003Cspan>Peshastin Mill Site\u003C/span>\u003C/a> isn't groomed on as rigorous a schedule as the other locations, but we aim to get out there once a week. It offers about a 3/4 mile jaunt that is and dog friendly and not requiring of a ski ticket.\u003C/p>"},"region":"Washington","country":"USA","regions":["US-WA-LWSC"],"groups":[{"groupId":"LeavenworthFatbike","groupName":"Snowshoe and Fat Bike Trails","groupBounds":[[-120.66916203384993,47.61290147190331],[-120.65347840553122,47.61919671262921]]},{"groupId":"LeavenworthSkiHill","groupOrder":1,"groupName":"Nordic Trails","groupBounds":[[-120.67192372266463,47.61229347190348],[-120.65398944253279,47.617746677074784]]}],"logo":"2024-07-05T10-39-54-820-06:00_US-WA-Leavenworth_logo.png","banner":"2024-12-01T11-58-39-075-07:00_US-WA-Leavenworth_Rob_0.jpg","lastGroomedClass":"twoWeeksAgo","active":true,"timezone":"America/Vancouver","liveTrack":true,"coordinates":[47.614260728497946,-120.66938766542918],"distance":11405.104227039186,"distanceGroups":[{"id":"easy","distance":5.61,"percent":49.19765942270223},{"id":"intermediate","distance":3.38,"percent":29.60266876147784},{"id":"advanced","distance":2.42,"percent":21.199671815819933}],"links":{"website":{"en":"https://skileavenworth.com/activities/nordic-skiing"},"weather":{"en":"https://www.yr.no/en/forecast/daily-table/47.614,-120.668"}},"testMode":true,"elevation":448,"lastTrailsUpdate":"2025-01-08T18:45:32.970Z","tempUnits":"F","timezoneUTC":"-7"},{"clubId":"US-CA-TahoeXC","season":"winter","activities":["nordic","snowshoe"],"countryId":"US","regionId":"CA","permalink":"Tahoe-XC","bounds":[[-120.17170974772716,39.1844383738831],[-120.10273497626767,39.21375121460468]],"lastGroomed":"2026-03-11T03:03:37.654Z","weatherSources":["680907e6e3004a71b66ca5f