e3004a71b66ca656"],"name":{"en":"Marcialonga"},"city":{"en":"Predazzo"},"description":{"en":"\u003Cdiv>\u003Cstrong>Marcialonga Track: the heart of cross-country skiing in the Dolomites\u003C/strong>\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv>&nbsp;\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv>The Marcialonga track winds its way through the heart of the Dolomites, crossing breathtaking alpine landscapes, charming villages, and snow-covered woods in the picturesque Fiemme and Fassa Valleys in Trentino. Stretching over 70 km in total, it is best known for hosting the namesake cross-country skiing marathon, held at the end of January when the entire route is skiable. During the rest of the winter season, the track remains operational in specific sections between Canazei and Molina.\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv>The track is also connected to the cross-country loops and ski centers of Canazei, Pozza di Fassa, and the Olympic Stadium in Lago di Tesero, making the area a prime destination for cross-country skiing enthusiasts.\u003C/div>","fr":"\u003Cdiv>\u003Cstrong>Piste Marcialonga : le c&oelig;ur du ski de fond dans les Dolomites\u003C/strong>\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv>&nbsp;\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv>La piste Marcialonga serpente au c&oelig;ur des Dolomites, traversant des paysages alpins spectaculaires, des villages pittoresques et des for&ecirc;ts enneig&eacute;es dans les magnifiques vall&eacute;es de Fiemme et de Fassa, dans le Trentin. Avec une longueur totale de plus de 70 km, elle est surtout c&eacute;l&egrave;bre pour accueillir la course de ski de fond &eacute;ponyme, qui se d&eacute;roule &agrave; la fin du mois de janvier, lorsque tout le parcours est praticable. Pendant le reste de la saison hivernale, la piste reste ouverte sur certains tron&ccedil;ons sp&eacute;cifiques entre Canazei et Molina.\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv>La piste est &eacute;galement reli&eacute;e aux boucles et centres de ski nordique de Canazei, Pozza di Fassa et au stade olympique de Lago di Tesero, faisant de la r&eacute;gion une destination incontournable pour les amateurs de ski de fond.\u003C/div>","de":"\u003Cdiv>\u003Cstrong>Marcialonga-Strecke: das Herz des Langlaufs in den Dolomiten\u003C/strong>\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv>&nbsp;\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv>Die Marcialonga-Strecke schl&auml;ngelt sich durch das Herz der Dolomiten und f&uuml;hrt durch atemberaubende alpine Landschaften, malerische D&ouml;rfer und verschneite W&auml;lder in den wundersch&ouml;nen T&auml;lern von Fiemme und Fassa im Trentino. Mit einer Gesamtl&auml;nge von &uuml;ber 70 km ist sie vor allem f&uuml;r den gleichnamigen Langlaufmarathon bekannt, der Ende Januar stattfindet, wenn die gesamte Strecke befahrbar ist. W&auml;hrend der restlichen Wintersaison bleibt die Strecke in bestimmten Abschnitten zwischen Canazei und Molina ge&ouml;ffnet.\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv>Die Strecke ist zudem mit den Langlaufrunden und Zentren von Canazei, Pozza di Fassa und dem Olympiastadion in Lago di Tesero verbunden, was die Region zu einem erstklassigen Ziel f&uuml;r Langlauffans macht.\u003C/div>"},"region":"Trentino","country":"Italy","logo":"2024-11-22T08-05-14-530-08:00_IT-TN-Marcialonga_logo_0.png","banner":"2024-11-22T08-04-29-734-08:00_IT-TN-Marcialonga_Rob_0.jpg","lastGroomedClass":"twoWeeksAgo","active":true,"timezone":"Europe/Paris","liveTrack":true,"coordinates":[46.328896568247856,11.60085492147242],"distance":82192.69459536405,"distanceGroups":[{"id":"easy","distance":57.65,"percent":70.13520945575739},{"id":"intermediate","distance":6.69,"percent":8.139291210802817},{"id":"advanced","distance":17.86,"percent":21.725499333439842}],"links":{"website":{"en":"https://www.marcialonga.it/marcialonga_ski/index_en.php"}},"elevation":1048,"lastTrailsUpdate":"2026-01-13T07:42:01.360Z","tempUnits":"C","timezoneUTC":"2","reportLatest":{"updatedAt":"2026-03-26T09:38:52.906Z","clubId":"IT-TN-Marcialonga","type":"grooming-report","content":{"en":"\u003Cp>🔴 tutte le piste chiuse... aspettiamo la primavera per tornare in ciclabile!\u003C/p>\n\n\u003Cp>🔴 all t