Mountain Trail Impacts&nbsp;\u003C/h5>\n\u003Cp>The City of Ketchum is building a new connector trail from Bald Mountain Trail to Warm Springs. There will be intermittent impacts to the first section of Bald Mountain Trail this summer. Please monitor check&nbsp;\u003Ca href=\"https://www.sunvalley.com/the-mountain/bald-mountain-terrain-updates/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://www.sunvalley.com/the-mountain/bald-mountain-terrain-updates/\u003C/a> for updates.&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Dollar Mountain Access Update:\u003C/strong>&nbsp;Sepp's Road is currently&nbsp;\u003Cstrong>closed\u003C/strong> from the top of Dollar Mountain to the top of Sepp's Bowl.\u003C/p>"},"account":"65556e472cde45640d8a8ce6","author":"Ashley","timestamp":"2026-06-30T17:44:00.000Z"},"reportNotices":[{"updatedAt":"2026-07-11T15:49:56.941Z","clubId":"US-ID-BCRD-BaldMountain","type":"grooming-report-notice","content":{"en":"\u003Cp>Wildlife closures have been lifted on Cold Springs and Warm Springs trails.&nbsp;\u003C/p>"},"account":"65556e472cde45640d8a8ce6","author":"Ashley","timestamp":"2026-07-01T14:00:16.000Z"}]},{"clubId":"US-ID-BCRD-Greenhorn","seasonSwitch":"US-ID-BCRD","season":"summer","activities":["nordic","ebike","equestrian","hiking","motorcycle","mtb"],"countryId":"US","regionId":"ID","permalink":"Greenhorn","bounds":[[-114.51993322226905,43.56614615929549],[-114.40836354004874,43.62317576019335]],"offlineMapsBounds":[[[[-114.52489870988735,43.574284202908856],[-114.49564285911507,43.574284202908856],[-114.49564285911507,43.56254871673547],[-114.49260609476073,43.56254871673547],[-114.49260609476073,43.55918506079937],[-114.46525717959554,43.55918506079937],[-114.46525717959554,43.56431834491227],[-114.40339707663763,43.56431834491227],[-114.40339707663763,43.590106257640336],[-114.39543987580261,43.590106257640336],[-114.39543987580261,43.6082607955814],[-114.40956108011676,43.6082607955814],[-114.40956108011676,43.61428338646701],[-114.4204965768076,43.6